# <a name="required-diagnostic-data-for-office"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-103">Nepieciešamie Office diagnostikas dati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-103">Required diagnostic data for Office</span></span>

> [!IMPORTANT]
> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-104">Informācija šajā rakstā attiecas uz tālāk minētās Office klienta programmatūras versiju 1904 vai jaunāku versiju, kas instalēta datorā, kurā darbojas sistēma Windows:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-104">The information in this article applies to Version 1904 or later of the following Office client software installed on a computer running Windows:</span></span>
> - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-105">Office 365 ProPlus un Office 365 Business</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-105">Office 365 ProPlus and Office 365 Business</span></span>
> - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-106">Office 365 individuālai lietošanai, Office 365 mājas lietošanai vai citas Office versijas, kas ir daļa no Office 365 abonementa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-106">Office 365 Personal, Office 365 Home, or other versions of Office that are part of an Office 365 subscription.</span></span>
> - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-107">Project un Visio, kas ir iekļautas dažos abonēšanas plānos, piemēram, Project Online Professional plānā vai Visio Online 2. plānā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-107">Project and Visio that come with some subscription plans, such as the Project Online Professional plan or Visio Online Plan 2.</span></span>
>
> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-108">Šī informācija attiecas arī uz tālāk norādīto sistēmas Office darbam ar Mac programmu versiju 16.28 vai jaunākām versijām: Excel, Outlook, OneNote, PowerPoint un Word.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-108">The information also applies to Version 16.28 or later of the following Office for Mac applications: Excel, Outlook, OneNote, PowerPoint, and Word.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-109">Diagnostikas dati tiek izmantoti, lai uzturētu Office drošu un atjauninātu, noteiktu, diagnosticētu un novērstu problēmas, kā arī uzlabotu produktu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-109">Diagnostic data is used to keep Office secure and up-to-date, detect, diagnose and fix problems, and also make product improvements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-110">Šie dati neietver lietotāja vārdu vai e-pasta adresi, failu saturu vai informāciju par programmām, kas nav saistītas ar Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-110">This data does not include a user’s name or email address, the content of the user’s files, or information about apps unrelated to Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-111">Šie diagnostikas dati tiek apkopoti un nosūtīti korporācijai Microsoft par Office klienta programmatūru, kas tiek lietota datoros, kuros darbojas operētājsistēma Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-111">This diagnostic data is collected and sent to Microsoft about Office client software being used on computers running Windows.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-112">Daži diagnostikas dati ir nepieciešami, bet daži diagnostikas dati ir neobligāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-112">Some diagnostic data is required, while some diagnostic data is optional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-113">Piedāvājam jums iespēju izvēlēties, vai sūtīt mums nepieciešamos vai neobligātos diagnostikas datus, izmantojot tādus konfidencialitātes kontroles līdzekļus kā organizācijas politikas iestatījumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-113">We give you the ability to choose whether to send us required or optional diagnostic data through the use of privacy controls, such as policy settings for organizations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-114">Mums sūtāmos diagnostikas datus varat skatīt, izmantojot diagnostikas datu skatītāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-114">You can see the diagnostic data being sent to us by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-115">***Nepieciešamie diagnostikas dati*** ir minimālie dati, kas nepieciešami, lai Office uzturētu drošu, atjauninātu un ar paredzēto veiktspēju atbilstošajā ierīcē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-115">***Required diagnostic data*** is the minimum data necessary to help keep Office secure, up-to-date, and performing as expected on the device it’s installed on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-116">Nepieciešamie diagnostikas dati palīdz noteikt ar Office saistītas problēmas, kuru cēlonis var būt saistīts ar ierīces vai programmatūras konfigurāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-116">Required diagnostic data helps to identify problems with Office that may be related to a device or software configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-117">Piemēram, tie var palīdzēt noteikt, vai Office līdzeklis biežāk avarē noteiktā operētājsistēmas versijā, kopā ar nesen ieviestiem līdzekļiem vai tad, kad ir atspējoti konkrēti Office līdzekļi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-117">For example, it can help determine if an Office feature crashes more frequently on a particular operating system version, with newly introduced features, or when certain Office features are disabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-118">Nepieciešamie diagnostikas dati palīdz mums ātrāk noteikt, diagnosticēt un novērst problēmas, lai mazinātu ietekmi uz lietotājiem vai organizācijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-118">Required diagnostic data helps us detect, diagnose, and fix these problems more quickly so the impact to users or organizations is reduced.</span></span>

## <a name="categories-and-data-fields-that-are-common-for-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-171">Kategorijas un datu lauki, kas ir kopīgi visiem notikumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-171">Categories and data fields that are common for all events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-172">Neatkarīgi no kategorijas vai datu apakštipa pastāv informācija par notikumiem, kas attiecas uz visiem notikumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-172">There is some information about events that is common to all events, regardless of category or data subtype.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-173">Šī kopīgā informācija, ko dažkārt dēvē par *datu līgumiem*, ir sakārtota kategorijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-173">This common information, which is sometimes referred to as *data contracts*, is organized into categories.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-174">Katrā kategorijā ir lauki, un šie lauki ir atsevišķa notikuma metadati un rekvizīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-174">Each category contains fields, and these fields are the metadata and properties of an individual event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-175">Šo informāciju varat skatīt, izmantojot diagnostikas datu skatītāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-175">You can view this information by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-176">Kategorijas, kurās ir apkopota informācija par notikumiem, var iedalīt divās grupās:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-176">The categories of information that is collected about events can be divided into two groups:</span></span>

  - [<span data-ttu-id="ef881-177">Informācija, kas ir kopīga visiem notikumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-177">Information common to all events</span></span>](#information-common-to-all-events)
  - [<span data-ttu-id="ef881-178">Informācija, kas īpaši atbalsta diagnostikas datu apkopošanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-178">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection</span></span>](#information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection)

### <a name="information-common-to-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-179">*Informācija, kas ir kopīga visiem notikumiem*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-179">*Information common to all events*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-180">Informācija, kas ir kopīga visiem notikumiem, tiek apkopota tālāk norādītajās kategorijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-180">Information common to all events is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="app"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-181">Programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-181">App</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-182">Informācija par lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-182">Information about the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-183">Visi lauki ir konstanti visām attiecīgās lietojumprogrammas versijas sesijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-183">All fields are constant for all sessions of a given application version.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-184">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-184">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-185">**Branch** — zars, no kura nāk attiecīgā būvējuma versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-185">**Branch** - The branch that the given build came from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-186">Ļauj mums noteikt, no kāda zara tipa nāk attiecīgais būvējums, lai mēs varētu pareizi piemērot labojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-186">Allows us to determine what type of branch a given build came from so that we can correctly target fixes.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-191">**Platform** — tās platformas plašā klasifikācija, kurā darbojas programma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-191">**Platform** - The broad classification of the platform on which the app is running.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-192">Ļauj mums noteikt platformas, kurās, iespējams, ir radusies problēma, lai mēs varētu pareizi noteikt problēmas prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-192">Allows us to identify on which platforms an issue may be occurring so that we can correctly prioritize the issue.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-253">Sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-253">Session</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-254">Informācija par procesa sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-254">Information about the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-255">Visi šīs sesijas lauki ir konstanti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-255">All fields are constant for this session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-256">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-256">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-257">**ABConfigs** — norāda testējamo variantu kopu, kas darbojas konkrētajā sesijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-257">**ABConfigs** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-258">Ļauj mums noteikt, kuri konkrētie testējamie varianti darbojas sesijā, lai mēs varētu noteikt, vai testējamā versija ir tās problēmas cēlonis, kas ietekmē lietotājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-258">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-259">**EcsETag** — indikators no testējamo variantu sistēmas, kas apzīmē mašīnai nosūtītos testējamos variantus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-259">**EcsETag** - An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-260">Ļauj mums noteikt, kuri testējamie varianti, iespējams, ietekmē attiecīgo sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-260">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-261">**Flags** — karodziņi, kas izseko bitmasku un attiecas uz visu sesiju. Pašlaik galvenā uzmanība tiek pievērsta iztveršanai un diagnostikas datu opcijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-261">**Flags** - Bitmask tracking flags applicable to an entire session, currently primarily focused on sampling and diagnostic data options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-262">Ļauj mums kontrolēt attiecīgās sesijas darbību saistībā ar sesijas ģenerētajiem diagnostikas datiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-262">Allows us to control how a given session behaves in relation to the diagnostic data that the session generates.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-263">**Id** — unikāli identificē attiecīgo datu sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-263">**Id** - Uniquely identifies a given session of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-264">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmu ietekmi, izvērtējot ietekmēto sesiju skaitu un nosakot, vai šīm sesijām ir kopīgi līdzekļi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-264">Allows us to identify the impact of issues by evaluating the number of sessions that are impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-265">**ImpressionId** — norāda testējamo variantu kopu, kas darbojas konkrētajā sesijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-265">**ImpressionId** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-266">Ļauj mums noteikt, kuri konkrētie testējamie varianti darbojas sesijā, lai mēs varētu noteikt, vai testējamā versija ir tās problēmas cēlonis, kas ietekmē lietotājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-266">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-267">**MeasuresEnabled** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai pašreizējie sesijas dati tiek iztverti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-267">**MeasuresEnabled** - Flag indicating if the current sessions data is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-268">Ļauj mums noteikt, kā statistiski izvērtēt datus, kas tiek apkopoti no attiecīgās sesijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-268">Allows us to determine how to statistically evaluate the data that is gathered from the given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-269">**SamplingClientId** — klienta ID, kas tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu, vai tas ir daļa no iztveršanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-269">**SamplingClientId** - The id of the client used to determine if it is part of sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-270">Ļauj mums noteikt, kāpēc konkrēta sesija tika iekļauta vai neiekļauta iztveršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-270">Allows us to determine why an individual session was included or excluded from sampling.</span></span>

#### <a name="user"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-271">Lietotājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-271">User</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-272">Sniedz komerciālās programmatūras SKU informāciju par nomnieku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-272">Provides tenant information for commercial software SKUs.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-273">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-273">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-274">**PrimaryIdentityHash** — identifikatora pseidonīms, kas apzīmē pašreizējo lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-274">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-275">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** — tās identitātes tips, kas atrodas šeit: PrimaryIdentityHash.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-275">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – The type of identity contained in the PrimaryIdentityHash.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-276">Kāds no MASCID, OrgIdCID vai UserObjectId.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-276">One of MASCID, OrgIdCID or UserObjectId.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-277">**TenantGroup** — tā nomnieka tips, kam pieder abonements.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-277">**TenantGroup** - The type of the tenant that the subscription belongs to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-278">Ļauj mums klasificēt problēmas un noteikt, vai problēma ir plaši izplatīta vai izolēta lietotāju kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-278">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-279">**TenantId** — nomnieks, ar kuru ir saistīts lietotāja abonements.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-279">**TenantId** - The tenant that a user’s subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-280">Ļauj mums klasificēt problēmas un noteikt, vai problēma ir plaši izplatīta vai izolēta konkrēta nomnieka lietotāju kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-280">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

### <a name="information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-281">*Informācija, kas īpaši atbalsta diagnostikas datu apkopošanu*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-281">*Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-282">Informācija, kas īpaši atbalsta diagnostikas datu apkopošanu, tiek apkopota tālāk norādītajās kategorijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-282">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="activity"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-283">Darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-283">Activity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-284">Informācija, lai izprastu paša pasākuma apkopošanas panākumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-284">Information to understand the success of the collection event itself.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-285">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-285">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-286">**AggMode** — nosaka, kā sistēmai jāapkopo darbības rezultāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-286">**AggMode** - Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-287">Ļauj mums samazināt no lietotāja mašīnas augšupielādētās informācijas apjomu, apkopojot darbības rezultātus vienā notikumā, kas tiek periodiski nosūtīts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-287">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user’s machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-288">**Count** — notikušās darbības reižu skaits, ja skaits ir no apkopotā notikuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-288">**Count** - The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-289">Ļauj mums noteikt, cik bieži darbība izdevās vai neizdevās, pamatojoties uz darbības apkopošanas režīmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-289">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-290">**CV** — vērtība, kas norāda relāciju starp darbībām un pakārtotajām darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-290">**CV** - A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-291">Ļauj mums atjaunot relāciju starp ligzdotajām darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-291">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-292">**Duration** — darbības izpildei nepieciešamais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-292">**Duration** - The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-293">Ļauj mums noteikt veiktspējas problēmas, kas negatīvi ietekmē lietotāju pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-293">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the users experience.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-294">**Result**.**Code** — lietojumprogrammas definēts kods, lai identificētu noteiktus rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-294">**Result**.**Code** - An application defined code to identify a given results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-295">Ļauj mums noteikt specifiskāku informāciju par konkrēto kļūmi, piemēram, kļūmes kodu, ko var izmantot, lai klasificētu un novērstu problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-295">Allows us to determine more specific details of a given failure such as a failure code that can be used to classify and fix issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-296">**Result.Tag** — vesela skaitļa tags, kas nosaka atrašanās vietu kodā, kurā tika ģenerēts rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-296">**Result.Tag** - An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the result was generated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-297">Ļauj mums skaidri noteikt atrašanās vietu kodā, kurā tika ģenerēts rezultāts, kas iespējo kļūmju klasifikāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-297">Allows us to distinctly identify the location in code where a result was generated which enables classification of failures.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-298">**Result**.**Type** — rezultāta koda tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-298">**Result**.**Type** - The type of the result code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-299">Norāda nosūtītā rezultātu koda tipu, lai varētu pareizi interpretēt vērtību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-299">Identifies what type of result code was sent so that the value can be correctly interpreted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-300">**Success** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai darbība izdevās vai neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-300">**Success** - A flag indicating if the activity succeeded or failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-301">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai lietotāja veiktās darbības produktā ir sekmīgas vai nesekmīgas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-301">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-302">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmas, kas ietekmē lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-302">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-310">**DistributionChannel** — kanāls, kurā ir izvietota programma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-310">**DistributionChannel** - The channel where the app was deployed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-311">Ļauj mums sadalīt ienākošos datus, lai mēs varētu noteikt, vai problēmas ietekmē auditoriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-311">Allows us to partition incoming data so we can determine if issues are impacting audiences.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-312">**InstallMethod** — vai pašreizējais Office būvējums tika jaunināts, atritināts vai instalēts no jauna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-312">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from an older build, rolled back to an older build, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-313">**IsClickToRunInstall** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai tika veikta Click-To-Run instalācija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-313">**IsClickToRunInstall** - Flag indicating if install was a click to run install.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-314">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmas, kas varētu būt specifiskas Click-To-Run instalēšanas mehānismam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-314">Allows us to identify issues that might be specific to the Click-To-Run install mechanism.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-315">**IsDebug** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai Office būvējums ir atkļūdošanas būvējums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-315">**IsDebug** - Flag indicating if the office build is a Debug build.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-316">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai problēmas rodas no atkļūdošanas būvējumiem, kas, iespējams, darbojas atšķirīgi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-316">Allows us to identify if issues are coming from Debug builds which may behave differently .</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-319">**IsOEMInstalled** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai Office instalēja oriģinālā aprīkojuma ražotājs (OEM).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-319">**IsOEMInstalled** - Flag indicating if Office was installed by an original equipment manufacturer (OEM).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-320">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai lietojumprogramma tika instalēta, izmantojot OEM. Tas mums var palīdzēt klasificēt un noteikt problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-320">Let’s us determine if the application was installed by an OEM which can help us classify and identify issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-321">**PreviousVersion** — Tā Office versija, kas bija iepriekš instalēta datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-321">**PreviousVersion** - The version of Office that was previously installed on the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-322">Ļauj atgriezties uz iepriekšējo versiju, ja pašreizējā versijā ir radusies problēma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-322">Allows us to roll back to a previous version if the current one has an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-323">**ProcessFileName** — lietojumprogrammas faila nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-323">**ProcessFileName** - The name of the application filename.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-324">Ļauj mums noteikt tās izpildāmā procesa nosaukumu, kas ģenerē datus, jo var būt vairāki dažādu procesu failu nosaukumi, kuriem ir tās pašas programmas nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-324">Allows us to identify the name of the executable which is generating the data as there may be several different process filenames reporting as the same app name.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-385">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-385">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-392">**Id** — unikāls notikuma identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-392">**Id** - A unique identifier for the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-393">Ļauj mums unikāli identificēt saņemtos notikumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-393">Allows us to uniquely identify the events that are being received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-394">**Name** — notikuma nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-394">**Name** - The name of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-395">Ļauj noteikt notikumu, kas tiek nosūtīts no klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-395">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-396">**Rule** — tās kārtulas identifikators, kas ģenerēja datus, ja tos ģenerēja kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-396">**Rule** - An identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-397">Ļauj mums noteikt datu avotu, lai mēs varētu pārbaudīt un pārvaldīt notikuma parametrus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-397">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-398">**RuleId** — tās kārtulas identifikators, kas ģenerēja datus, ja tos ģenerēja kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-398">**RuleId** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-399">Ļauj mums noteikt datu avotu, lai mēs varētu pārbaudīt un pārvaldīt notikuma parametrus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-399">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-400">**RuleInterfaces** — jebkurš interfeiss, kuru ievieš konkrēta kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-400">**RuleInterfaces** - Any interfaces that are implemented by the specific rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-401">Ļauj mums klasificēt un importēt datus atbilstoši to struktūrai, kas vienkāršo datu apstrādi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-401">Allows us to classify and import the data based on its structure which simplifies data processing.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-402">**RuleVersion** — tās kārtulas identifikators, kas ģenerēja datus, ja tos ģenerēja kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-402">**RuleVersion** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-403">Ļauj mums noteikt datu avotu, lai mēs varētu pārbaudīt un pārvaldīt notikuma parametrus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-403">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-404">**SampleRate** — norāda, cik liels lietotāju skaits (procentos) sūta šos datus. Tas ļauj mums veikt datu statistisko analīzi un nodrošina, ka ne visiem lietotājiem ir jānosūta biežāk izmantotie datu punkti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-404">**SampleRate** - An indication of what percentage of users are sending this piece of data This allows us to do statistical analysis of the data and for very common data points not require that to be sent by all users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-405">**SchemaVersion** — tās shēmas versija, kas tiek izmantota, lai ģenerētu diagnostikas datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-405">**SchemaVersion** - The version of the schema used to generate diagnostic data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-406">Nepieciešama, lai pārvaldītu datus, kas tiek sūtīti no klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-406">Required to manage data being sent form the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-407">Tādējādi laika gaitā var mainīt, kādi dati tiek sūtīti no katra klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-407">This allows changes over time in what data is being sent from each client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-408">**Sequence** — skaitītājs, kas identificē secību, kādā tika ģenerēts notikums klientā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-408">**Sequence** - A counter that identifies the order that an event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-409">Ļauj kārtot saņemtos datus, lai mēs varētu noteikt darbības, kas, iespējams, izraisīja problēmu, kas ietekmē klientus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-409">Allows the data being received to be ordered so that we can identify what steps may have led to an issue that is impacting clients.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-410">**Source** — avota kanāls, kas tika izmantots, lai augšupielādētu datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-410">**Source** - The source pipeline that was used to upload the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-411">Nepieciešams, lai pārraudzītu mūsu augšupielādes kanālu vispārējo darbspēju un palīdzētu noteikt problēmas saistībā ar augšupielādes kanālu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-411">Required to monitor each of our upload pipelines for overall health and to help identify issues with the upload pipeline.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-412">Tas ļauj kontrolēt atsevišķus augšupielādes kanālus, lai nodrošinātu to atbilstību prasībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-412">This allows us to monitor individual upload pipelines to make sure they remain compliant.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-413">**Time** — laiks, kad klientā tika ģenerēts notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-413">**Time** - The time that the event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-414">Ļauj mums sinhronizēt un pārbaudīt to notikumu secību, kas ir ģenerēti klientā, kā arī izveidot veiktspējas rādītājus lietošanas norādījumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-414">Allows us to synchronize and validate the order of events generated on the client as well as establish performance metrics for user instructions.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-439">**DisableTelemetry** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai ir iestatīta atslēga DisableTelemetry.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-439">**DisableTelemetry** - Flag indicating if the DisableTelemetry key is set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-440">Ļauj mums uzzināt, vai sesija ziņo par citiem diagnostikas datiem, kas nav EssentialServiceMetadata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-440">Allows us to know if a session was not reporting diagnostic data other than EssentialServiceMetadata.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-441">**SamplingKey** — atslēga, kas tiek izmantota, lai noteiktu, vai sesija ir iztverta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-441">**SamplingKey** - The key used to determine whether the session is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-442">Ļauj mums saprast, kā atsevišķas sesijas izvēlas savu iztveršanas statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-442">Allows us to understand how individual sessions are making their choice of whether they are sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-443">**SamplingMethod** — metode, kas tiek izmantota, lai noteiktu iztveršanas politiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-443">**SamplingMethod** - The method used to determine sampling policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-444">Ļauj mums saprast, kādi dati nāk no sesijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-444">Allows us to understand what data is coming from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-445">**Sequence** — unikāls skaitlisks sesijas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-445">**Sequence** - A unique numeric identifier for the session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-446">Ļauj kārtot sesijas, lai analizētu iespējamās problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-446">Allows the ordering of sessions for analysis of then issues might have occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-447">**Start** — procesa sesijas palaišanas laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-447">**Start** - The boot time of the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-448">Ļauj mums noteikt sesijas sākumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-448">Allows us to establish when the session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-449">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** — starpība minūtēs starp UTC un vietējo laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-449">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** - The difference in minutes between UTC and the local time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-450">Ļauj normalizēt UTC laiku atpakaļ uz vietējo laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-450">Allows normalization of UTC times back to the local time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-451">**SamplingClientIdValue** — tās atslēgas vērtība, kas tiek izmantota iztveršanas noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-451">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-452">Ļauj mums noteikt, kāpēc tika iztverta (vai neiztverta) sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-452">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-453">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** — tās atslēgas vērtība, kas tiek izmantota iztveršanas noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-453">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-454">Ļauj mums noteikt, kāpēc tika iztverta (vai neiztverta) sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-454">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** — papildu iztveršanas metadati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-456">Izmanto, lai palīdzētu novērtēt saņemto datu statistikas nozīmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-456">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** — papildu iztveršanas metadati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-458">Izmanto, lai palīdzētu novērtēt saņemto datu statistikas nozīmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-458">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-459">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** — vērtība, kas norāda, kāda līmeņa diagnostikas datiem ir piekritis lietotājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-459">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** - Value indicating what level of diagnostic data the user has opted into.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-460">Ļauj mums saprast, kāda līmeņa diagnostikas datus var sagaidīt no sesijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-460">Allows us to understand what level of diagnostic data to expect from a session.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-onenote-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-461">OneNote notikumiem kopīgie datu lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-461">Data fields that are common for OneNote events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-462">Zemāk norādītie datu lauki ir kopīgi visiem OneNote notikumiem Mac, iOS un Android operētājsistēmās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-462">The following data fields are common for all events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-465">**Activity_ActivityType** —  norāda uz šīs darbības notikuma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-465">**Activity_ActivityType** -  Indicates the type of this activity event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-466">Darbība var būt normāla vai augstvērtīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-466">An activity can be a normal activity or a high value activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-467">**Activity_AggMode** —  norāda sistēmai, kā apkopot darbības rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-467">**Activity_AggMode** -  Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-468">Ļauj mums samazināt no lietotāja mašīnas augšupielādētās informācijas apjomu, apkopojot darbības rezultātus vienā notikumā, kas tiek periodiski nosūtīts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-468">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user’s machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-469">**Count** — notikušās darbības reižu skaits, ja skaits ir no apkopotā notikuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-469">**Activity_Count** -  The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-470">Ļauj mums noteikt, cik bieži darbība izdevās vai neizdevās, pamatojoties uz darbības apkopošanas režīmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-470">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-473">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** — laiks, kad darbība ir dīkstāvē un faktiski neveic darbu, bet šis laiks joprojām ieskaitītas darbības kopējā laikā.  </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-473">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time an activity is idle and not doing any real work, but the time is still count towards the total activity's time.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-474">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** — darbības izpildei nepieciešamais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-474">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-475">Ļauj mums noteikt veiktspējas problēmas, kas negatīvi ietekmē lietotāju pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-475">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the users experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-476">**Activity_Expiration** — datums skaitliskā formātā, kas norāda laiku, kad šis notikums pārtrauks sūtīšanu no klientiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-476">**Activity_Expiration** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-477">**Activity_FailCount** — darbības neizdošanās reižu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-477">**Activity_FailCount** -  A number of times this activity has failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-478">**Activity_Name** — īss notikuma nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-478">**Activity_Name** -  A short name of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-479">Ļauj noteikt notikumu, kas tiek nosūtīts no klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-479">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-480">**Activity_Namespace** — notikuma nosaukumu apgabals.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-480">**Activity_Namespace** -  A namespace of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-481">Ļauj grupēt notikumu grupās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-481">Allows to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-482">**Activity_Reason** — virkne, kas norāda uz iemeslu, kura dēļ darbība beidzas ar konkrēto rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-482">**Activity_Reason** -  A string indicating the reason causing an activity to ends with a particular result.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-493">**EventName** — unikāls OneNote notikuma nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-493">**EventName** -  A unique name of a OneNote's event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-494">Pagātnes inženierijas ierobežojumu dēļ, OneNote notikumi izmanto šo pielāgoto lauku unikālā nosaukuma norādīšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-494">OneNote events use this custom field to specify a unique name due to an engineering limitation in the past.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-567">**audienceGroup** — laidiena auditorijas grupas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-567">**audienceGroup** - The release audience group name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-568">**audienceId** — laidiena auditorijas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-568">**audienceId** - The release audience name</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingensurecached"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-622">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-622">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-623">Izseko, vai tika lejupielādēta dinamiskās pamatnes pakotne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-623">Tracks if a package for Dynamic Canvas was downloaded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-624">Tiek uzskatīta par programmatūras konfigurāciju, jo pakotne ir sekmīgi jālejupielādē, lai iespējotu klientu atveidot pareizās iespējas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-624">Considered a software configuration because the package must be successfully downloaded to enable the client to render the right experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-625">Tas ir īpaši būtiski patērētāju abonementos, kur mēs izmantojam pamatni, lai paziņotu lietotājam par licences derīguma termiņa beigām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-625">Is especially critical in consumer subscriptions where we use canvas to communicate to the user that the license has expired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-626">Izmanto, lai izsekotu produkta lejupielādētās un kešotās dinamiskā satura pakotnes metadatiem, kā arī to darbību rezultātiem, kam tika pakļauta pakotne: lejupielādes kļūmēm, pakotnes atvēršanas kļūmēm, konsekvences pārbaudes kļūmēm, kešatmiņas trāpījumiem, pakotnes lietojumam un lejupielādes avotiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-626">Used to track metadata of a dynamic content package downloaded and cached by the product as well as results of operations performed on the package: download failures, unpacking failures, consistency checks failures, cache hits, package usages, download sources.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-627">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-627">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-628">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated —** Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, vai izdevās izveidot kešatmiņas mapi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-628">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated -** Boolean flag indicating if cache folder creation succeed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-629">**Data\_CdnPath — pakotnes avota adrese —**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-629">**Data\_CdnPath – source address of the package-**</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-630">**Data\_EnsureCached —** Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, vai tika kešota satura pakotne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-630">**Data\_EnsureCached -** Boolean flag indicating if content package was cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-631">**Data\_ExistsAlready —** Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, ka pakotne jau tika iepriekš lejupielādēta un pastāv vēl viens lejupielādes mēģinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-631">**Data\_ExistsAlready -** Boolean flag indicating that the package was already downloaded before and there was another attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-632">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed —** avota pakotne nav pieejama avotā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-632">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed -** source package not available in source</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-633">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder —** lokālā diska problēmas, kas izraisa kļūmes direktorija izveides laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-633">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder -** local disk issues causing failure in directory creation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-634">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed —** karodziņš, kas norāda, vai pakotne ir lejupielādēta, bet klients nevar to nolasīt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-634">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed -** flag indicating if package was downloaded, but the client can’t read it</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-635">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess —** veiksmīgi mēģinājumi lasīt pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-635">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess -** successful attempts to read the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-636">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess —** nepastāv neviena ar disku vai konfigurāciju saistīta problēma, kas neatļauj lasīt failu plūsmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-636">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess -** no disk issues nor configuration issues which doesn’t let the file stream to be read</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-637">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed —** relatīvais ceļš nenorāda uz pieejamu atrašanās vietu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-637">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed -** relative path doesn’t point to accessible location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-638">**Data\_HashActualValue —** jaukšanas vērtība, kas tika iegūta no faila nosaukuma, lietojot pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-638">**Data\_HashActualValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-639">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed —** jaukšanas aprēķina kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-639">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed -** error with calculation of a hash</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-640">**Data\_HashMatchFailed —** jaukšanas neatbilstība starp pakotnes nosaukumu un kešotajām reģistra vērtībām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-640">**Data\_HashMatchFailed -** hash mismatch between the package name and registry values cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-641">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess —** sekmīga jaukšanas konsekvences pārbaude</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-641">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess -** hash consistency check success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-642">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed —** nevar lejupielādēt pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-642">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed -** can’t download the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-643">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData —** lejupielādētajā pakotnē nav datu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-643">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData -** downloaded package contains no data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-644">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess —** sekmīgi lejupielādēta pakotne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-644">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess -** successful download of a package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-645">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess —** pakotnes atvēršanas mēģinājumu statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-645">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess -** unpacking attempts statuses</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-646">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed —** nesekmīgie pakotnes faila atvēršanas mēģinājumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-646">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed -** failed attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-647">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess —** sekmīgie pakotnes faila atvēršanas mēģinājumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-647">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess -** successful attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-648">**Data\_SuccessHashValue —** jaukšanas vērtība, kas tika iegūta no faila nosaukuma, lejupielādējot pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-648">**Data\_SuccessHashValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was downloaded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-649">**Data\_SuccessSource —** virsma, kam tika lejupielādēta pakotne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-649">**Data\_SuccessSource -** surface for which the package was downloaded</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidodwxpssotelemetry"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1227">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1227">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1228">Šis notikums palīdz izprast, ar kuru citu Microsoft lietojumprogrammu ierīcē mūsu lietojumprogramma saņēma kluso pierakstīšanos, no kura ieejas punkta un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1228">This event helps in understanding with which other Microsoft app in the device, our app got silent single sign on, from which entry point and so on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1229">Palīdz izprast klusās pierakstīšanās kļūmes iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1229">Also helps in understanding the failure reason for not getting silent single sign on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1230">Mēs saņemam plašāku ieskatu par to, no kuras Microsoft lietojumprogramma ierīcē mēs saņemam vienotu pierakstīšanās pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1230">We get better insights like from which Microsoft app in the device, we are getting single sign on experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1231">Rīkoties reaģējot uz kļūmēm, kad vienotā pierakstīšanās nedarbojas, kā paredzēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1231">Act upon failures, where single sign on is not working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1232">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1232">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1233">**AccountType** — norāda konta veidu, ar kuru notiek vienotā pierakstīšanās, piemēram, personiskais Microsoft konts vai darba konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1233">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which single sign on is happening, like personal Microsoft account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1234">**EntryPoint** — norāda ieejas punktu lietojumprogrammā, no kura tika uzsākts vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1234">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where single sign on attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1235">**ErrorCode** — norāda vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma kļūdas kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1235">**ErrorCode** - Indicates the error code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1236">**ErrorDescription** — norāda vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma kļūdas ziņojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1236">**ErrorDescription** - Indicates the error message of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1237">**HResult**— norāda vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma rezultāta statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1237">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1238">**ProviderPackageId** — cita Microsoft lietojumprogramma ierīcē, no kuras notiek vienotā pierakstīšanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1238">**ProviderPackageId** - Other Microsoft app in the device from which single sign on is happening.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidphonenumbersignins"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1239">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1239">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1240">Šis notikums palīdz saprast, vai lietotājs ir pierakstījies vai pierakstījies ar tālruņa numuru saistītu kontu, vai ar personisko e-astu saistītu Microsoft kontu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1240">This event helps in understanding if user signed in or signed up with phone number-based account or email based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1241">Šis notikums palīdz noteikt lietotāju pierakstīšanos vai reģistrāciju ar mobilo tālruņa numuru saistītu personisko Microsoft kontu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1241">This event helps in knowing count of users signing in or signing up with phone number based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1242">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1242">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1243">**EntryPoint** — norāda ieejas punktu lietojumprogrammā, no kura tika uzsākts pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1243">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1244">**IsEmailMissing** — vai konta profila informācijā trūkst e-pasta adreses?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1244">**IsEmailMissing** - Is email missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1245">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** — vai konta profila informācijā trūkst tālruņa numura?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1245">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** - Is phone number missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1246">**UserDecision** — norāda lietotāja veikto izvēli, piemēram, pierakstīšanās vai reģistrācija, vai pierakstīties vēlāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1246">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidusersignindecision"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1247">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1247">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1248">Šis notikums palīdz saprast, kura posmā lietotājs pārtrauc pierakstīšanās plūsmu, kāpēc pierakstīšanās neizdodas, cik daudz lietotājiem izdodas veiksmīgi pierakstīties no kura lietojumprogrammas ieejas punkta un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1248">This event helps in understanding at which stage user is dropping in sign in flow, why sign in is failing, how many users are getting signed in successfully from which entry point in the app and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1249">Šis pasākums palīdz ar pierakstīšanās piltuves datiem, kas palīdz saprast, kurā posmā rodas kļūmes lielākam lietotāju skaitam un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1249">This event helps with sign-in funnel data, which helps in understand at which stage users are getting dropped more and so on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1250">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1250">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1251">**AccountType** — norāda konta veidu, ar kuru notiek pierakstīšanās mēģinājums, piemēram, personiskais konts vai darba konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1251">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which sign-in is attempted like personal account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1252">**AfterLicensingState** — norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas statusu pēc pierakstīšanās pabeigšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1252">**AfterLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state after sign-in completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1253">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** — norāda bezmaksas rediģējumu skaitu pirms pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1253">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** - Indicates how many free edits have lapsed before sign-in was attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1254">**BeforeLicensingState** — norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas statusu pirms pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1254">**BeforeLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state before sign-in attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1255">**CompletionState** — norāda pierakstīšanās pabeigšanas posmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1255">**CompletionState** - Indicates the stage of sign-in completion.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1256">**EntryPoint** — norāda ieejas punktu lietojumprogrammā, no kura tika uzsākts pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1256">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1257">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** — norāda uz paātrinātās pierakstīšanās mēģinājumu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1257">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1258">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** — norāda uz atcelto paātrinātās pierakstīšanās mēģinājumu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1258">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups cancelled.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1259">**HResult** — norāda pierakstīšanās darbības rezultāta statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1259">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the sign-in operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1260">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** — vai pierakstīšanās ar tālruņa numuru ir atļauta?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1260">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** - Is phone number-based sign-in allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1261">**LicenseActivationHResult** — norāda licences aktivizēšanas mēģinājuma statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1261">**LicenseActivationHResult** - Indicates the status code of license activation attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1262">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** — norāda licencēšanas pakalpojuma ziņojuma kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1262">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** - Indicates the message code from licensing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1263">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** — vai bezmaksas rediģēšana ir atļauta?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1263">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** - Is free edits allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1264">**SignUpAttemptCount** — norāda uz pierakstīšanās mēģinājumu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1264">**SignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1265">**StartMode** — norāda režīmu, kurā tika sākts pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1265">**StartMode** - Indicates the mode in which sign-in attempt was started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1266">**UserDecision** — norāda lietotāja veikto izvēli, piemēram, pierakstīšanās vai reģistrācija, vai pierakstīties vēlāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1266">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1267">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1267">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1268">Tiek ģenerēts klienta palaišanas laikā, ja gala lietotājs ir iespējojis Office telemetrijas informācijas paneli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1268">Generated on client startup when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1269">Apkopo informāciju par to, kad Office telemetrijas aģents augšupielādē datus koplietošanas mapē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1269">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent has uploaded data to the share folder.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1270">Šī notikuma primārais izmantošanas veids ir uzraudzīt Office telemetrijas aģenta stāvokli, bet sekundārais izmantošanas veids ir noteikt Office telemetrijas informācijas paneļa izmantošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1270">The primary use of this event is to monitor the health of the Office Telemetry agent and the secondary use of the event is to estimate usage of the Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1271">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1271">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1355">**DataSource_Name** — pievienoto datu avota nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1355">**DataSource_Name** - Name of connected data source</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docs_apple_docsuxiossaveasthroughfilemenu"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1360">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1360">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1361">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1361">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1362">Pasākumu ieraksti, veicot darbību "Saglabāt kā" un tiek izmantoti, lai izprastu un noteiktu lietotāja pieredzes prioritāti, pamatojoties uz failu darbības informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1362">The event records when a “Save as” operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1363">Darbība "Saglabāt kā" tiek veikta katru reizi, kad lietotājs izveido jaunu failu un saglabā to pirmo reizi vai saglabā esošā faila kopiju jaunajā atrašanās vietā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1363">A “Save as” operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1364">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1364">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1365">**Data_OriginServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt. un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1365">**Data_OriginServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the original location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1366">**Data_ServiceType** — abstrakta jaunās atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana pēc saglabāšanas, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt. un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1366">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the new location of a file after the save is completed like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1368">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1368">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1369">Šis notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs "@" piemin citu lietotāju un izmanto, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritāti lietotāja pieredzei, pamatojoties uz to, kā lietotāji sadarbojas ar citiem lietotājiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1369">This event records when a user “@” mentions another user and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on how users collaborate with other users.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docs_apple_docsuxmacodspsharingwebviewsharingcompleted"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1372">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1372">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1373">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1373">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1374">Šis notikums ieraksta, ja lietotājs izvēlas koplietot mākoņa dokumentu, izmantojot OneDrive koplietošanas pieredzi, un tas tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1374">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1375">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1375">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1376">**Data_ShareType** — stingri kodēta virkne, kas norāda, kāda veida kopīgošanas darbība ir pabeigta, tostarp, bet ne tikai, "Kopēt saiti", "Citas programmas", "Teams".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1376">**Data_ShareType** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share operation was completed including but not limited to “Copy Link”, “More apps”, “Teams”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1377">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** — stingri kodēta virkne, kas norāda, kāda veida kopīgošana bija aktīva, kad kopīgošana bija pabeigta, ieskaitot ne tikai "Piekļuves pārvaldība", "@pieminēšana", "Kopīgot".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1377">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share mode was active when the share was completed including but not limited to “ManageAccess”, “AtMentions”, “Share”.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1379">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1379">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1380">Šī notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs atlasa, lai aplūkotu pašreizējo līdzautoru sarakstu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1380">This event records when a user selects to look at the list of current co-authors.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1381">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotājam, kas saistīti ar dokumentu vienlaicīgu koprediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1381">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to co-authoring a document at the same time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1382">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1382">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1383">**Data_CoauthorCount** — skaitliska vērtība, kas apzīmē kopējo personu skaitu, kuras pašlaik rediģē to pašu dokumentu, ko lietotājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1383">**Data_CoauthorCount** - A numerical value that represents the total number of people who are currently editing the same document as the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1390">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** — līdzautoru skaits, kas pameta dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1390">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** - The number of co-authors that left the document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1393">**Data_ServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1393">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1395">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1395">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1396">Notikums ieraksta, kad tiek izveidots jauns fails, no darbības "Jauns no veidnes", un to izmanto, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzei, pamatojoties uz dokumentu izveides informāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1396">The event records when a new file is created from the “New from template” experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on document creation information.</span></span>
