- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1399">**Data_InSearch** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai fails tika izveidots, kad lietotājs meklēja veidni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1399">**Data_InSearch** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1400">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja cilne Sākums pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1400">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1401">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja pieredze "Ieteicams" pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1401">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the “Recommended” experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1402">**Data_TemplateIndex** — veidnes faila skaitliskais indekss, kas tiek rādīts vizuāli lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1402">**Data_TemplateIndex** - The numerical index of the template file as it is displayed visually to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1403">**Data_TemplateType** — klasifikācija, kas palīdz atšķirt veidnes tipu, piemēram, bet ne tikai "Tiešsaistes" veidnes, "Tiešsaistes meklēšanas" veidnes, "Lokālās" veidnes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1403">**Data_TemplateType** - A classification to help distinguish the type of template like, but not limited to, “Online” templates, “Online search” templates, “Local” templates.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_docstage_recommendedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1404">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_RecommendedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1404">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_RecommendedOpen</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1405">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1405">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1406">Notikums ieraksta, ja fails tiek atvērts, izmantojot dokumentu galerijas ieteicamo failu sadaļas, un tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāju pieredzei, pamatojoties uz informāciju par failu atvēršanas darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1406">The event records when a file-open operation takes place from the recommended files section of the document gallery and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1407">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1407">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1408">**Data_Success** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai operācija bija sekmīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1408">**Data_Success** - A Boolean value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_docsuifileopenmacrequired"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1409">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1409">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1410">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1410">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1411">Notikums ieraksta, kad notiek failu atvēršanas darbība, un tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz failu atvēršanas informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijas "Pakalpojuma tips" un paplašinājuma pirmās četras rakstzīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1411">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1412">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1412">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1413">**Data_Ext** — faila paplašinājums attiecas tikai uz pirmajiem četriem paplašinājuma simboliem vai mazāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1413">**Data_Ext** - The file extension limited to the first four characters of the extension or less.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1414">**Data_ServiceType** — faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1414">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_opendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1415">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1415">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1416">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammām, kas darbojas iOS platformā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1416">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1417">Notikuma ieraksti brīdī, kad notiek faila atvēršanas darbība, tiek izmantoti, lai saprastu un noteiktu prioritāti lietotāju pieredzēm, balstoties uz informāciju par faila atvēršanu, it īpaši veiktspējas informāciju. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1417">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1418">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1418">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1419">**Data_AppDuration** — lietojumprogrammā, kas veic faila atvēršanu, pavadītais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1419">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1420">**Data_BootDuration** — faila atvēršanas palaišanas procesa ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1420">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of boot process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1421">**Data_ClickOrigin** — virkne, kas norāda uz saites daļas izcelsmi brīdī, kad lietotājs noklikšķināja uz saites iOS Outlook, lai atvērtu failu Office lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1421">**Data_ClickOrigin** - A string indicating which part the link was from when user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open a file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1422">**Data_ClickTime** — Unix diskretizācijas laiks, kad lietotājs noklikšķināja uz saites iOS Outlook, lai atvērtu failu Office lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1422">**Data_ClickTime** - The Unix epoch time when the user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open the file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1423">**Data_DetachedDuration** — notikuma atvienošanas procesa ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1423">**Data_DetachedDuration** - The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1424">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila piekļuves režīmu, piemēram, tikai lasāms, lasāms-rakstāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1424">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1425">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind**— uzskaitījums, kas norāda asinhronās plūsmas veidu, kas tika izmantota faila atvēršanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1425">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1426">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila dalīšanas algoritma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1426">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1427">**Data_Doc_EdpState** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila uzņēmuma datu aizsardzības statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1427">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1428">**Data_Doc_Ext** — faila paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1428">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1429">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** — faila servera resursdatora nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1429">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1430">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera resursdatora nosaukumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1430">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1431">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē identitāti, kas tika izmantota, lai atvērtu failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1431">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1432">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda detalizēto faila atvēršanas darbības scenārija veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1432">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1433">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila atvēršanas darbības ievadizvades karodziņus, piemēram, vai fails ir kešots.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1433">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1434">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** — vai failam ir iespējota sadarbība mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1434">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1435">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** — vai fails tika atvērts ar inkrementālo atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1435">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1436">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** — vai fails atbalsta Office sadarbības pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1436">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1437">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** — vai fails tiek atvērts no bezsaistes kešatmiņas kopijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1437">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1438">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** — vai fails tika iepriekš ielādēts pirms atvēršanas darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1438">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1439">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** — vai mākonī esošajam failam ir lokālā versija un, vai tā ir sinhronizēta ar serveri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1439">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1440">**Data_Doc_Location** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila atrašanās vietu, piemēram, atrodas lokāli vai mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1440">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1441">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila tikai lasīšanas iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1441">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1442">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē faila servera resursa ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1442">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1443">**Data_Doc_RtcType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila izmantotā reāllaika kanāla (RTC) veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1443">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1444">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera dokumenta ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1444">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1445">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera protokolu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1445">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1446">**Data_Doc_ServerType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1446">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1447">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1447">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1448">**Data_Doc_SessionId** — vesels skaitlis, kas pieaug par 1 ar katru faila atvēršanas darbību sesijas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1448">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1449">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** — virkne, kas tiek izmantota, lai savstarpēji saistītu klienta un servera žurnālus; parasti tas ir kāds ID veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1449">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1450">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** — dokumenta lielums baitos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1450">Data**Size:long** - File size in bytes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1451">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda īpašās rakstzīmes veidu faila URL adresē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1451">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1452">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē faila URL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1452">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1453">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** — norāda, vai fails tika atvērts inkrementāli, izmantojot iepriekš kešotus WRS datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1453">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre-cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1454">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** — virkne, kas norāda, no kura pakalpojuma ir WOPI (tīmekļa lietojumprogrammas atvērtās platformas interfeisa protokols) fails.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1454">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a WOPI (Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1455">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** — virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumā pavadīto laiku formātā ar funkcijas birku un ilgumu, kas iekļauj apakšfunkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1455">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1456">**Data_InitializationReason** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila atvēršanas veidu, piemēram, no lietotāja interfeisa elementa vai citas lietojumprogrammas izsaukuma rezultātā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1456">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, e.g. from which UI element or trigged by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1457">**Data_Measurements** — virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumā pavadīto laiku formātā ar funkcijas birku un ilgumu, kas neiekļauj apakšfunkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1457">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1458">**Data_OpenInPlace** — vai fails ir jākopē Office smilškastes konteinerā, pirms lietotājs var to atvērt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1458">**Data_OpenInPlace** - Whether or not a file must be copied to the Office’s sandboxed container before user can open it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1459">**Data_OpenStartTime** — Unix diskretizācijas laiks, kad tika sākta faila atvēršana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1459">**Data_OpenStartTime** - The Unix epoch time when the file open started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1460">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** — faila atvēršanas renderēšanas ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1460">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1461">**Data_SourceApplication** — virkne, kas norāda avota lietojumprogrammas komplekta ID, kad faila atvēršanu uzsāk cita lietojumprogramma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1461">**Data_SourceApplication** - A string indicating the bundle ID of the source application when a file open was triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1462">**Data_StopwatchDuration** — laiks no notikuma sākuma līdz notikuma beigām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1462">**Data_StopwatchDuration** - The duration from beginning of the event to the end of the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1463">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements**— virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu formātā ar funkcija birku, sākuma laikspiedolu un ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1463">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_openfilewithreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1464">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1464">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1465">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1465">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1466">Notikums ieraksta, kad notiek failu atvēršana, un tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz failu atvēršanas informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijas "Pakalpojuma tips" un no kurienes lietotājs pieprasīja atvērt failu programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1466">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and from where within Application the user requested to open a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1467">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1467">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1468">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** — šī ir Būla vērtība, kas tiek reģistrēta, ja, pārbaudot faila ceļu, mūsuprāt, tas var būt no mapes, kas tiek sinhronizēta ar Dropbox.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1468">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** - This is a Boolean value that is logged if by inspecting the path of the file we think it might be from a folder that is sync’d by Drop Box.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1469">**Data_IsSignedIn** — neatkarīgi no tā, vai tiek pierakstīts lietotājs, kad fails ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1469">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1470">**Data_OpenReason** — atvērtais iemesls ir skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, no kurienes programmā lietotājs ir atvēris failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1470">**Data_OpenReason** - The open reason is a numerical value that indicates from where within the application a user opened a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1471">**Data_ServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1471">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract numerical categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_savetourl"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1472">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1472">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1473">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1473">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1474">Notikums ieraksta, kad notiek darbība "saglabāt kā", un tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz failu darbības informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijas un paplašinājuma pirmās četras rakstzīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1474">The event records when a “save as” operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1475">Darbība "Saglabāt kā" tiek veikta katru reizi, kad lietotājs izveido jaunu failu un saglabā to pirmo reizi vai saglabā esošā faila kopiju jaunā atrašanās vietā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1475">A “save as” operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1476">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1476">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1477">**Data_FileExtension** — pirmās četras rakstzīmes jaunā faila paplašinājumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1477">**Data_FileExtension** - The first four characters of the new file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1478">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** — norāda, vai saglabāšanas darbība ir paredzēta jaunam failam vai esoša faila kopijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1478">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** - Indicates if the save operation is for a new file or a copy of an existing file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1479">**Data_IsSignedIn** — neatkarīgi no tā, vai tiek pierakstīts lietotājs, kad fails ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1479">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1480">**Data_SaveErrorCode** — skaitliska vērtība, kas ir iestatīta, ja ir kļūda, kas palīdz noteikt kļūdas veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1480">**Data_SaveErrorCode** - A numerical value that is set if there is an error to help identify the kind of error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1481">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** — norāda tā SaveErrorCode domēnu, ko Apple SaveErrorCode domēns definē kā "patvaļīgas virknes, kas tiek izmantotas, lai diferencētu kodu grupas".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1481">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** - Specifies the domain of the SaveErrorCode as defined by Apple SaveErrorDomains “are arbitrary strings used to differentiate groups of codes”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1482">**Data_SaveLocation** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1482">**Data_SaveLocation** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1483">**Data_SaveOperationType** — skaitliska vērtība, ko definē Apple NSSaveOperationType vērtību grupa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1483">**Data_SaveOperationType** - A numerical value defined by Apple’s NSSaveOperationType group of values.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1484">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1484">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1485">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1485">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1486">Šis notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs dodas caur dokumentu papildu pārdošanai uz mākoņa plūsmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1486">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1487">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotājam, kas saistītas ar dokumentu vienlaicīgu koprediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1487">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1488">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1488">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1489">**Data_FileStyle** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, kādā scenārijā papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika parādīta kā no automātiskās saglabāšanas slēdža vai kopīgošanas pogas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1489">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like from an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1490">**Data_FileType** — pirmās četras rakstzīmes pašreizējā faila paplašinājumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1490">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1491">**Data_InDocStage** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tiek parādīta dokumentu galerijā vai dokumenta logā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1491">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai ir atvērts pašreizējais dokuments, kurā redzama papildu pārdošanas pieredze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1493">**Data_IsDraft** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai pašreizējais fails kaut kad ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1493">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1494">**Data_IsSheetModal** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika prezentēta modāli vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1494">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1495">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1495">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1496">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1496">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1497">Šis notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs izvēlas augšupielādēt jaunu vai lokālo failu mākonī un šīs darbības rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1497">This event records when a user chooses to upload a new or local file to the cloud and the result of that operation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1498">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotājam, kas saistītas ar dokumentu vienlaicīgu koprediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1498">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1499">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1499">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1500">**Data_FileStyle** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, kādā scenārijā papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika parādīta kā no automātiskās saglabāšanas slēdža vai kopīgošanas pogas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1500">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1501">**Data_FileType** — pirmās četras rakstzīmes pašreizējā faila paplašinājumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1501">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1502">**Data_InDocStage** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tiek parādīta dokumentu galerijā vai dokumenta logā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1502">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1503">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai atlasītā atrašanās vieta, kur augšupielādēt dokumentu, ir noklusējuma atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1503">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** - A Boolean value that indicates if the selected location to upload the document to is the default location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1504">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai ir atvērts pašreizējais dokuments, kurā redzama papildu pārdošanas pieredze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1504">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1505">**Data_IsDraft** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai pašreizējais fails kaut kad ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1505">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1506">**Data_IsSheetModal** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika prezentēta modāli vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1506">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1507">**Data_LocationServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1507">**Data_LocationServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1508">**Data_UploadAction** — cietā kodētā virkne, kas norāda, vai augšupielāde bija pārvietošanas vai kopēšanas darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1508">**Data_UploadAction** - A hard coded string that indicates whether the upload was a move or a copy operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1509">**Data_UploadResult** — cieta kodēta virkne, kas norāda mēģinājuma rezultātu, tostarp, bet ne tikai, "Izdevās", "UserCancelledUpload" un "PreAuthFailed".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1509">**Data_UploadResult** - A hard coded string that indicates the result of the attempt to upload including but not limited to ‘’Success”, “UserCancelledUpload”, and “PreAuthFailed”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_copylinkoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1510">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CopyLinkOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1510">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CopyLinkOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1511">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1511">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1512">Šī notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs izvēlas kopīgot dokumentu, ģenerējot saiti uz mākoņa dokumentu, un tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1512">This event records when a user chooses to share a document by generating a link to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1513">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1513">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1514">**Data_ ServiceType** — abstrakta faila atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., nevis faktiskā faila atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1514">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1515">**Data_LinkType** — cietā kodētā virkne, kas apraksta uzaicināšanas darbības veidu, piemēram, "ViewOnly" un "ViewAndEdit".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1515">**Data_LinkType** - A hard coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like “ViewOnly” and “ViewAndEdit”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1516">**Data_ShareScenario** — iekodēts virknes apraksts, kur programmas lietotāja interfeisā fails tiek koplietots, ieskaitot, bet neaprobežojoties ar "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1516">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_docsuionedriveshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1517">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1517">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1518">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1518">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1519">Šis notikums ieraksta, ja lietotājs izvēlas koplietot mākoņa dokumentu, izmantojot OneDrive koplietošanas pieredzi, un tas tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1519">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1520">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1520">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1521">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** — Ja koplietošanas pieredze atklāj kļūdu, tā ir skaitliska vērtība, kas palīdz noteikt kļūmes iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1521">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** - If the sharing experience experiences an error this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1522">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ka vieglā koplietošanas darbība ir sekmīgi pabeigta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1522">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** - A Boolean value that when true indicates that a lightweight sharing operation successfully completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1523">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** — ja kopīgošanas darbība ir veiksmīgi pabeigta, šī ir skaitliska vērtība, kas tiek lietota, lai noteiktu, kāda veida koplietošanas darbība tika pabeigta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1523">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** - When a share operation successfully completes this is a numerical value used to determine what kind of sharing operation was completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1524">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** — ja lietotāja interfeiss nav ielādēts, šī ir skaitliska vērtība, kas palīdz identificēt kļūmes iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1524">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** - If the user interface fails to load this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1525">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** — skaitliska vērtība, kas ieraksta, cik daudz laika ir nepieciešams, lai tīmekļa lietotāja interfeiss tiktu ielādēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1525">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** - A numerical value that records the amount of time it took for the web user interface to load.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_invitepeople"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1526">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1526">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1527">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1527">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1528">Šis notikums ieraksta, ja lietotājs izvēlas uzaicināt lietotājus uz mākoņa dokumentu un tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1528">This event records when a user chooses to invite people to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1529">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1529">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1530">**Data_ ServiceType** — abstrakta faila atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., nevis faktiskā faila atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1530">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1531">**Data_InviteeCount** — kopējais kontaktpersonu skaits, kas uzaicināti uz dokumentu vienā uzaicinājuma darbībā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1531">**Data_InviteeCount** - The total number of contacts invited to a document in one invite action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1532">**Data_LinkType** — cietā kodētā virkne, kas apraksta uzaicināšanas darbības veidu, piemēram, "ViewOnly" un "ViewAndEdit".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1532">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like “ViewOnly” and “ViewAndEdit”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1533">**Data_MessageLength** — uzaicinājuma ziņojumā nosūtīto rakstzīmju kopējais skaitlisks skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1533">**Data_MessageLength** - A numerical count of the total number of characters sent in the invite message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1534">**Data_ShareScenario** — cieti kodēts virknes apraksts, kur programmas lietotāja interfeisā fails tiek koplietots, ieskaitot, bet ne tikai "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1534">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_sendacopyoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1535">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1535">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1536">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1536">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1537">Notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs izvēlas sūtīt dokumenta kopiju, un tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1537">The event records when a user chooses to send a copy of a document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1538">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1538">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1539">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja cilne Sākums pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1539">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1540">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja pieredze "Ieteicams" pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1540">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the “Recommended” experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1541">**Data_OperationType** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, kāda veida kopijas nosūtīšanas darbība tiek veikta, piemēram, nosūtot kopiju e-pastā vai nosūtot kopiju, izmantojot Apple kopīgošanas vadību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1541">**Data_OperationType** - A numerical value to indicate what kind of send a copy operation is taking place like sending a copy in an email or sending a copy through Apple’s share control.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1542">**Data_ServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1542">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1543">**Data_ShareFileType** — cietais kodētais virknes apraksts par to, kāda tipa objektu koplieto, tostarp, bet ne tikai, "Dokuments", "PDF", "Attēls".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1543">**Data_ShareFileType** - A hard coded string description of what type of object is being shared including but not limited to, “Document”, “PDF”, “Picture”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1544">**Data_ShareScenario** — cieti kodēts virknes apraksts, kur programmas lietotāja interfeisā fails tiek koplietots, ieskaitot, bet ne tikai "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1544">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1545">**Data_SharingService** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai fails tika izveidots, kad lietotājs meklēja veidni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1545">**Data_SharingService** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_upsellshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1546">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1546">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1547">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1547">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1548">Šis notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs dodas caur dokumentu papildu pārdošanai uz mākoņa plūsmu, mēģinot kopīgot dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1548">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow when trying to share a document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1549">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, kas saistīta ar dokumentu pārvietošanu uz mākoņa vietām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1549">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1550">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1550">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1551">**Data_FileOperationResult** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, vai operācija bija sekmīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1551">**Data_FileOperationResult** - A numerical value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1552">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai lietotājs izmanto papildu pārdošanu, lai izveidotu mākoņa plūsmu no DocStage pieredzes vai atvērta dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1552">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** - A Boolean to indicate if a user is going through the upsell to cloud flow from the DocStage experience or from an open document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1553">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai, ja izmantojat, izvēlējās saglabāt lokālu dokumentu, kas tiek augšupielādēts mākoņa atrašanās vietā, vai pārvietojat esošo dokumentu uz mākoņa atrašanās vietu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1553">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** - A Boolean to indicate if the use chose to keep a local copy of the document being uploaded to a cloud location or move the existing document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1554">**Data_NewFileType** — faila jaunas atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1554">**Data_NewFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of the new location of the file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1555">**Data_OriginalFileType** — abstrakta faila atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., nevis faktiskā faila atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1555">**Data_OriginalFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1556">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai lietotājs ir izvēlējies augšupielādēt pašreizējo dokumentu mākoņa atrašanās vietā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1556">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** - A Boolean to indicate if the user chose to upload the current document to a cloud location.</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsisavefilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1708">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1708">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1709">Ļauj uzzināt, vai fails ir veiksmīgi saglabāts no FIO līmeņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1709">Allows us to know if a file was successfully saved from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1710">Izmanto līdzekļu darbspējas veicināšanai un pārraudzībai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1710">Used for Feature Health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1711">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1711">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

#### <a name="officefindtimeappfailedtostart"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-1855">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1855">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1856">Apkopo, ja programmu nevar palaist, jo startēšanas laikā radās neparedzēta kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1856">Collected when app fails to start due to an unexpected error during startup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1857">Izmantot, lai izsekotu izņēmumiem un avārijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1857">Used to track exceptions & crashes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1858">Palīdz pārraudzīt un atkļūdot programmas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1858">Helps monitor & debug app health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-1859">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1859">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-1860">**DateTime** — notikuma reģistrēšanas laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-1860">**DateTime** - Timestamp of when the event is logged</span></span>

    - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2025">**networkEffectiveType** — efektīvā tīkla savienojuma tips, piemēram, "slow-2g Online", lai noteiktu, vai lietotājam ir izveidots savienojums ar internetu brīdī, kad tiek parādīta personas kartīte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2025">**networkEffectiveType** - The effective type of network connection, e.g. "slow-2g Online” to identify whether the user is connected to the internet at the time of showing the persona card</span></span>

    - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2027">**personaCorrelationId** — globāli unikāls identifikators unikālajām personām sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2027">**personaCorrelationId** - A globally unique identifier for unique personas in a session</span></span>

    - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2029">**wasOpenedAsCompactCard** — izmanto, lai noteiktu, vai kartīte sākotnēji tika atvērta kā kompakts skats</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2029">**wasOpenedAsCompactCard** - Used to identify if the card was opened as a compact view initially</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2050">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** — noklusējuma kanvas tālummaiņas faktors.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2050">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** - Default Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2051">**InkStrokeCount** — kopējais rokraksta vilkumu skaits kopš pēdējā žurnāla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2051">**InkStrokeCount** - Total count of ink strokes since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2069">**TriggerInfo** — norāda papildu informāciju par trigeri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2069">**TriggerInfo** - Indicates additional information related to the trigger.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2118">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pirmo atbilstošo rezultātu atzīmju meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2118">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2119">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pēdējo atbilstošo rezultātu atzīmju meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2119">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2120">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** — norāda vidējo laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu visus atbilstošo rezultātus atzīmju meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2120">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2121">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pirmo atbilstošo rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2121">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2123">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** — norāda vidējo laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu visus atbilstošo rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2123">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2124">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (iOS operētājsistēmā), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (Android operētājsistēmā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2124">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2125">Šis ir kritisks signāls, kas tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu līmpiezīmju lietotāju iespēju programmā izveidot piezīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2125">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2126">Telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2126">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2127">Ja lietotājiem neizdodas izveidot piezīmi, tā aktivizēs kritisku incidentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2127">If users can’t create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2128">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2128">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2130">**IsExportable** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai šis notikums bija lietotāja darbības rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2130">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2131">Jābūt iestatītam kā “True”, jo “NoteCreated” ir lietotāja izraisīta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2131">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2132">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** — versijas numurs, kurā norādīta lietotāja izmantoto līmpiezīmju versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2132">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2133">Ļauj mums noteikt, kurās produkta versijās ir radusies problēma, lai mēs varētu pareizi noteikt tās prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2133">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2142">**NoteLocalId** — atšķirams unikāls identifikators, kas piešķirts piezīmei laikā, kad lietotājs izveido piezīmi programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2142">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2143">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** — versijas numurs, kurā norādīta lietotāja izmantoto līmpiezīmju versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2143">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2144">Ļauj mums noteikt, kurās produkta versijās ir radusies problēma, lai mēs varētu pareizi noteikt tās prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2144">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2145">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2145">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2148">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2148">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2149">**CachedError_Code** — ciparu vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2149">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2150">**CachedError_Description** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas apraksts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2150">**CachedError_Description** -a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2151">**CachedError_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2151">**CachedError_Tag** -indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2152">**CachedError_Type** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u. tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2152">**CachedError_Type** -the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2153">**ExecutionTime** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai replicētu piezīmju grāmatiņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2153">**ExecutionTime** -time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2154">**Gosid** — globālais objektu telpas ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2154">**Gosid** -global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2155">**IdentityType** — identitātes tips, piemēram, Windows Live, organizācijas ID utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2155">**IdentityType** -identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2156">**InitialReplicationInSession** — norāda, vai šī replicēšana ir pirmā piezīmju grāmatiņas replicēšana pēc atvēršanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2156">**InitialReplicationInSession** -is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2161">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūda ir neparedzēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2161">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** -is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2163">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūda bija paredzēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2163">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** -is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2164">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizēšana notiek, izmantojot moderno lapas satura sinhronizāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2164">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** -is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2165">**LastAttemptedSync** — laikspiedols, kad piezīmju grāmatiņu tika mēģināts sinhronizēt iepriekšējo reizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2165">**LastAttemptedSync** -timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2166">**LastBackgroundSync** — laikspiedols, kad notika pēdējais mēģinājums veikt sinhronizāciju fona režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2166">**LastBackgroundSync** -timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2169">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** — norāda, vai sinhronizācija ir jārestartē, jo pastāv nekonsekvences.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2169">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** -does the sync need to restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2170">**NotebookErrorCode** — piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūdas kods, kas saglabāts piezīmju grāmatiņas diagrammas apgabalā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2170">**NotebookErrorCode** -notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2171">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2171">**NotebookId** -notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2172">**NotebookType** — piezīmju grāmatiņas tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2172">**NotebookType** -notebook type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2173">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** — norāda, vai sinhronizācija tiek restartēta nekonsekvenču dēļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2173">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** -does the sync restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2174">**SectionError_Code** — numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2174">**SectionError_Code** -a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the section sync error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2175">**SectionError_Description** — sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūdas apraksts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2175">**SectionError_Description** -a description of the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2176">**SectionError_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2176">**SectionError_Tag** -indicate where in the code throws the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2178">**Success** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizācija izdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2178">**Success** -is the notebook sync successful or not</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2272">Apkopo, kad ir aizvērtas PowerPoint prezentācijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2272">Collected when PowerPoint presentations are closed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2273">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek, izmantojot aizvēršanas procesu, kas ietver lietotāja datu turpināšanu un sinhronizēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2273">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the close process which entail persisting and syncing the user's data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2274">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka aizvēršana darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2274">Microsoft uses this data to ensure that close is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2275">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2275">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2276">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long —** vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data\_Doc\_\* lauki)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2276">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2277">Ja tā nav, kāpēc?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2277">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2278">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string —** vai pastāv iepriekš noteiktu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokumentā tika atspējota automātiskā saglabāšana?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2278">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string -** Predefined set of values of why was autosave disabled on this document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2279">(Sapludināšanas kļūda, saglabāšanas kļūda, grupas politika utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2279">(Merge error, Save error, Group policy etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2280">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** Kā tika veikta aizvēršana?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2280">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** How was close performed?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2281">Aizverot dokumentu?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2281">Closing document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2282">Aizverot programmu?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2282">Closing app?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2283">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long —** neapstrādāto izņēmumu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2283">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Number of unhandled exceptions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2284">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long —** darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2284">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2285">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long —** kā šis dokuments ir atvērts (tikai lasāms | lasīšana un rakstīšana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2285">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2286">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2286">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2287">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2287">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2288">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long —** kā dokuments ir saglabāts pakalpojumā SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2288">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2289">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long —** dokumenta uzņēmuma datu aizsardzība statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2289">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2290">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2290">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2292">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long —** iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2292">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2296">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string —** tās identitātes unikālais identifikators, kas tika izmantota koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2296">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2298">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2298">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2299">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool —** patiess, ja "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP galvene jau ir saņemta no pieprasījuma OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2299">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>
