  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2341">**Data\_UserContinuedZRTClose:bool —** vai, aizverot dokumentu, lietotājs izvēlējās "Turpināt", lai aizvērtu?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2341">**Data\_UserContinuedZRTClose:bool -** Upon showing dialog on close, did user selected ‘Continue’ to close?</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationnewdocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2342">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2342">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2343">Apkopo, kad PowerPoint izveido jaunu prezentāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2343">Collected when PowerPoint creates a new presentation.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2344"> Ietver panākumus un veiktspējas rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2344"> Includes success failure and performance metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2345">Šī informācija tiek izmantota, lai mēs varētu sekmīgi izveidot failus, nepasliktinot veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2345">This information is used to ensure we can create files successfully and with no degradation in performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2346">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2346">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2347">**NewDocumentType** — vai jaunais dokuments ir izveidots no veidnes vai vienkārši izveidots tukšs?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2347">**NewDocumentType** – Whether new document is created from template or just created blank?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2348">**FLifeguarded** — vai dokuments ir aizsargāts (līdzeklis, kas atjauno bojāta dokumenta statusu, nepaziņojot par to lietotājam)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2348">**FLifeguarded** – Is document life guarded (feature that restores corrupt document state without prompting user)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationopencompleteprotocol"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2349">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2349">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2350">Apkopo, kad PowerPoint atver prezentācijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2350">Collected when PowerPoint opens presentations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2351">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek pēdējos atvēršanas procesa posmos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2351">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the end stages of the open process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2352">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu līdzekļa pareizu darbību un neietekmētu prezentāciju atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2352">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and there is no degradation to opening presentations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2353">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2353">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2354">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa pretvīrusu programmatūras skenēšanas tipam (IOAV, AMSI, nav utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2354">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long -** Predefined set of values of type of AntiVirus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2356">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool —** vai dokuments tika aizvērts un atkārtoti atvērts?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2356">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool -** Was this document closed and reopened?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2357">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long —** darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2357">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2358">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long —** kā šis dokuments ir atvērts (tikai lasāms | lasīšana un rakstīšana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2358">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2359">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2359">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2360">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2360">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2361">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long —** kā dokuments ir saglabāts pakalpojumā SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2361">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2362">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long —** dokumenta uzņēmuma datu aizsardzība statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2362">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2363">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2363">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2364">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2364">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2365">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long —** iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2365">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2366">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string —** dokumentu glabāšanas vieta (SharePoint.com, live.net), pieejama tikai Office 365 domēniem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2366">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2367">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string —** dokumenta glabāšanas vietas jaukšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2367">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2369">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string —** tās identitātes unikālais identifikators, kas tika izmantota koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2369">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2370">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long —** bitmaska dažādiem ar IO saistītiem karodziņiem, kas attiecas uz dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2370">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2371">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2371">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2372">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool —** patiess, ja "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP galvene jau ir saņemta no pieprasījuma OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2372">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2373">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool —** vai dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli (jauns līdzeklis, kas atver dokumentu bez vajadzības lejupielādēt visu dokumentu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2373">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2377">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda dokumenta glabāšanas vietu (lokālā, SharePoint, WOPI, tīkls utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2377">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2380">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda veidu, kā dokuments ir šifrēts ar paroli (nav, parole lasīšanai, parole rediģēšanai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2380">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2383">**Data_Doc_RtcType —** norāda, kā reāllaika kanāls (RTC) bija iestatīts pašreizējam failam (atspējots, neatbalstīts, pēc pieprasījuma, vienmēr ieslēgts utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2383">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsave"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2409">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2409">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2410">Apkopots ikreiz, kad PowerPoint veic saglabāšanu, izmantojot modernu koda ceļu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2410">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the modern code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2411">Ietver saglabāšanas veiktspējas rādītāju rezultātu tipa panākumus un saistītos dokumenta metadatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2411">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2412"> Saglabāšanas kļūmes var izraisīt datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2412"> Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2413">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka līdzeklis darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2413">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2414">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2414">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2415">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long —** vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data\_Doc\_\* lauki)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2415">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2416">Ja tā nav, kāpēc?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2416">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2417">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika ģenerēts dokuments pirms saglabāšanas notikuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2417">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long -** Time taken to raise Document Before Save Event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2418">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long —** cik ilga laikā tika pārbaudīta pārskatīšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2418">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to check revision</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2419">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long —** cik ilga laikā tika saglabāts makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2419">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to save macros</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2420">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika noņemts automātiskās saglabāšanas karodziņš</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2420">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear AutoSave flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2421">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika noņemts mainīta dokumenta karodziņš</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2421">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear document dirty flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2422">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika klonēts dokuments pirms saglabāšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2422">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clone document before starting the save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2423">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika izpildīta saglabāšanas darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2423">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long -** Time taken to commit the save transaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2424">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long —** nenotverti vietējie izņēmumi darbības izpildes laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2424">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2427">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2427">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2428">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2428">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2433">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long —** iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2433">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2437">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string —** tās identitātes unikālais identifikators, kas tika izmantota koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2437">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2439">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2439">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2448">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda veidu, kā dokuments ir šifrēts ar paroli (nav, parole lasīšanai, parole rediģēšanai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2448">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2449">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc šis dokuments ir atzīmēts kā tikai lasāms (bloķēts serverī, pabeigts dokuments, aizsargāts ar paroli rediģēšanai utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2449">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2451">**Data_Doc_RtcType —** norāda, kā reāllaika kanāls (RTC) bija iestatīts pašreizējam failam (atspējots, neatbalstīts, pēc pieprasījuma, vienmēr ieslēgts utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2451">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2453">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kurš protokols tiek izmantots, lai sazinātos ar serveri (HTTP, Cobalt, WOPI utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2453">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2495">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2495">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2496">Apkopots ikreiz, kad PowerPoint veic darbību Saglabāt kā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2496">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a Save As.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2497">Ietver saglabāšanas veiktspējas rādītāju rezultātu tipa panākumus un saistītos dokumenta metadatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2497">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2498">Saglabāšanas kļūmes var izraisīt datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2498">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2499">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka līdzeklis darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2499">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2500">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2500">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2501">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** — vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data_Doc_\* lauki)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2501">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2502">Ja nav, kāpēc?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2502">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2503">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** — darbības izpildes laikā nenotvertie vietējie izņēmumi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2503">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2504">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** — darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2504">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2505">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** — kā šis dokuments tika atvērts (tikai lasāms | lasīšana un rakstīšana).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2505">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2506">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2506">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2507">\*\*Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta jaunā mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2507">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the new cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2508">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** — kā dokuments ir saglabāts pakalpojumā SharePoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2508">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2509">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** — dokumenta uzņēmuma datu aizsardzība statuss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2509">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** - Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2510">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** — dokumenta paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2510">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2511">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** — dokumenta paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2511">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2512">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** — iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2512">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** - Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2513">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** — dokumentu glabāšanas vieta (SharePoint.com, live.net), pieejama tikai Office 365 domēniem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2513">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2514">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** — dokumenta glabāšanas vietas jaukšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2514">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** - Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2516">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** — koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai izmantotās identitātes unikālais identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2516">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** - Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2517">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** — bitmaska dažādiem ar IO saistītiem karodziņiem, kas attiecas uz dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2517">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** - Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2518">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2518">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** - Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2519">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** — patiess, ja "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP galvene jau ir saņemta no pieprasījuma OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2519">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** - True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2520">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool**— vai dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli (jauns līdzeklis, kas atver dokumentu bez vajadzības lejupielādēt visu dokumentu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2520">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** - Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2522">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** — pārbauda, vai dokuments tiek atvērts no lokālās kešatmiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2522">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** - verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2523">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** — vai dokuments tiek atvērts no mapes, kas izmanto OneDrive sinhronizācijas programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2523">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** - Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2524">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda dokumenta glabāšanas vietu (lokālā, SharePoint, WOPI, tīkls utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2524">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** - Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2527">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda veidu, kā dokuments ir šifrēts ar paroli (nav, parole lasīšanai, parole rediģēšanai).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2527">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** - Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2528">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc šis dokuments ir atzīmēts kā tikai lasāms (bloķēts serverī, pabeigts dokuments, aizsargāts ar paroli rediģēšanai utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2528">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2537">**Data_DstDoc_SizeInBytes:long** — dokumenta lielums baitos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2537">**Data_DstDoc_SizeInBytes:long** - Document size in bytes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2593">Apkopots ikreiz, kad PowerPoint veic saglabāšanu, izmantojot mantotā koda ceļu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2593">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the legacy code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2594">Ietver saglabāšanas veiktspējas rādītāju rezultātu tipa panākumus un saistītos dokumenta metadatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2594">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2595">Saglabāšanas kļūmes var izraisīt datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2595">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2596">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka līdzeklis darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2596">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2597">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2597">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2601">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** — darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2601">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptmacshellprintinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2730">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Mac.Shell.PrintInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2730">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Mac.Shell.PrintInfo</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2731">Tiek apkopots katru reizi, kad tiek veikta PDF eksportēšanas darbība, un satur informāciju par darbības rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2731">Collected whenever an export PDF operation has completed and contains information about the success of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2732">Mūsu lietojumprogrammā šī informācija ir kritiski svarīga PDF eksportēšanas darbību veiksmīgas izpildes noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2732">This information is critical to identify the success of export PDF operations for our application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2734">**Data_ExportAsPDFSucceed** — būla, kas norāda, ka PDF eksportēšana bija veiksmīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2734">**Data_ExportAsPDFSucceed** - Boolean indicating if exporting as PDF was a success.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2736">Svarīgs PowerPoint līdzeklis, kas apkopo kļūmes slaidrādes laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2736">Collecting failures during slide show as a key feature for PowerPoint.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2737">Microsoft apkopo datus par kļūdām slaidrādes laikā, lai palīdzētu uzlabot slaidrādes lietošanas iespējas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2737">Microsoft is collecting when error happens during slide show to help improve user experience on slide show.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2738">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai iegūtu diagnostikas informāciju par vietu, kur notika kļūda, kamēr lietotājs izmantoja slaidrādi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2738">Microsoft uses this data to get diagnostic information about where the error happens while user is using slide show.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2740">**CountOArtErrors** — kopējais OArt kļūdu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2740">**CountOArtErrors** - total number of OArt errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2741">**CountOtherErrors** — kopējais pārējo kļūdu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2741">**CountOtherErrors** - total number of other errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2742">**CountPPTErrors** — kopējais PPT kļūdu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2742">**CountPPTErrors** - total number of PPT errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2743">**CountSlideShowErrors** — kopējais slaidrādes kļūdu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2743">**CountSlideShowErrors** - total number of slide show errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2744">**FirstOArtError** — pirmā OArt kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2744">**FirstOArtError** - first error happened in OArt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2745">**FirstOtherError** — pirmā kļūda citā apgabalā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2745">**FirstOtherError** - first error happened in other area</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2746">**FirstPPTError** — pirmā PPT kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2746">**FirstPPTError** - first error happened in PPT</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2888">Apkopo tās atlases tulkojuma panākumus, kuru izraisīja lietotāja darbība, izmantojot tulkošanas SDX.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2888">Collects success or failure of a selection translation that a user action triggers in the Translator SDX.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2889">Tas ir svarīgi, lai novērtētu tulkošanas līdzekļa darbspēju un reaģētu uz iespējamiem darbības pārtraukumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2889">This is critical to evaluate the health of the translation feature and react to any outages that might occur.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2890">Izmanto, lai pārraudzītu atlases tulkošanas scenārija darbspēju programmā Excel, PowerPoint un Word.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2890">Used to monitor the health of the "Translate Selection" scenario in Excel, PowerPoint, Word.</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedfeatureexperimentation"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2944">Office.Visio.Shared.FeatureExperimentation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2944">Office.Visio.Shared.FeatureExperimentation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2948">**Data\_Enable:bool**— patiess norāda, ka līdzeklis ir iespējots pašreizējam lietotājam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2948">**Data\_Enable:bool**- true indicate the feature is enabled for current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2950">**Data\_Flighted:bool** — patiess norāda, ka šis līdzeklis ir iespējots</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2950">**Data\_Flighted:bool** - true indicates the feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2951">**Data\_Licensed:bool** — patiess norāda, ka šim līdzeklim tiek veikta licences pārbaude</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2951">**Data\_Licensed:bool** - true indicates the feature is under licensing check</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2952">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam ir abonementa licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2952">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** - true indicates the user has subscription license</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2960">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** — patiess, ja lietotājs atlasīja shēmas pārrakstīšanas opciju atsvaidzināšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2960">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** - true if user selected overwrite diagram option during refresh</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2961">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** — patiess, ja lietotājam tika parādīts brīdinājums datu atsvaidzināšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2961">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** - true if there was any warning shown to user during data refresh</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedwritebacktoexcel"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2962">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2962">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2970">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** — formu skaits, kas izdzēstas pārrakstīšanas laikā Excel funkcionalitātē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2970">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** - Number of shapes deleted during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2971">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājs atlasīja datu pārrakstīšanas opciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2971">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** - true indicate user selected overwrite data option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2972">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** — patiess norāda, ka tiek mainīti avota dati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2972">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** - true indicates source data is modified</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2973">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts datu atjaunināšanas brīdinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2973">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** - true means data update warning shown to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2974">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts brīdinājums, jo programmā Excel ir ievietota formula</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2974">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user because of presence of formula in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2975">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts brīdinājums, jo programmā Excel trūkst nākamās darbības identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2975">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** - true indicates warning show to the user because next step Identifier missing in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2976">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts brīdinājums, lai pārvērstu Excel datus tabulas formātā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2976">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user to convert Excel data to table format</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfilenewcreatenewfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2977">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2977">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2978">Šis notikums norāda, ka ir izveidots jauns Office Word dokuments un seko šīs darbības panākumu statusam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2978">This event indicates that a new document is created in Office Word and tracks success or failure of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2979">Notikums tiek izmantots, lai pārraudzītu jaunā dokumenta izveides pareizu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2979">The event is used to monitor that new document creation is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2980">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2980">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2981">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2981">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2982">**Data\_DirtyState** — vai dokuments tika izveidots mainītā statusā (ar nesaglabātām izmaiņām)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2982">**Data\_DirtyState** - whether the document was created in a dirty state (with changes that need to be saved)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2983">**Data\_ErrorID** — identifikators darbības kļūmes gadījumā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2983">**Data\_ErrorID** - error identifier in case of operation failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2984">**Data\_MainPdod —** dokumenta identifikators šī procesa laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2984">**Data\_MainPdod** - The document identifier during this process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2985">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** — norāda, vai dokuments ir izveidots, izmantojot pielāgotu veidni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2985">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** - indicates whether the document was created from a custom template</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenuserinitiatedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-2986">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2986">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2987">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu pēc lietotāja iniciētas darbības, nevis izmantojot Office Word programmiski.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2987">This event indicates Office Word opens a document by user initiation instead of by Office Word programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2988">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2988">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2989">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2989">The event monitors whether file-open is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2990">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2990">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="ef881-2991">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2991">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2992">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2992">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2993">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2993">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2994">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2994">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2995">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2995">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2996">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2996">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2997">**Data_BytesUnknown**— baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2997">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2998">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2998">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-2999">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-2999">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3000">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3000">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3001">**Data_Doc_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3001">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3002">**Data_Doc_Ext —** dokumenta paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3002">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3003">**Data_Doc_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3003">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3004">**Data_Doc_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3004">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3005">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash —** klientu identificējama domēna nosaukuma vienvirziena jaukšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3005">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3006">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId —** tādas lietotāja identitātes vienvirziena jaukšana, kas tiek izmantota atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3006">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3007">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario —** dokumenta atvēršanas ieraksti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3007">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3008">**Data_Doc_IOFlags —** atskaites par kešotajiem karodziņiem, kas tiek izmantoti atvēršanas pieprasījuma opciju iestatīšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3008">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3009">**Data_Doc_IrmRights —** dokumentam/lietotājam piemērotās elektronisko datu politikas atļautās darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3009">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactcmdgosubsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3053">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3053">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3054">Šis notikums norāda, ka lietotājs saglabā izmaiņas jaunā dokumentā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3054">This event indicates that a user is saving their changes to a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3055">Notikums pārrauga jauna dokumenta saglabāšanas pareizu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3055">The event monitors whether saving to a new document is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3056">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3056">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3057">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3057">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3060">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3060">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3061">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3061">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3062">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3062">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3064">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3064">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3065">**Data_Doc_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3065">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3066">**Data_Doc_Ext —** dokumenta paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3066">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3067">**Data_Doc_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3067">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3068">**Data_Doc_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3068">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactfconfirmsavedoccorequerysave"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3103">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3103">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3104">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word aicina lietotāju saglabāt izmaiņas, kad tiek mēģināts aizvērt dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3104">This event indicates Office Word prompts the user to save changes when it tries to close the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3105">Tas ļauj korporācijai Microsoft pārraudzīt, vai saglabāšana pēc programmas aizvēršanas darbojas pareizi un netiek zaudēti dati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3105">It allows Microsoft to monitor whether save-at-quit works as expected to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3106">Notikums pārrauga, vai dokumenta saglabāšana pēc programmas aizvēršanas darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3106">The event monitors whether save-at-quit is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3107">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3107">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3108">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3108">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3109">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3109">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3110">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3110">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3111">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3111">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3112">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3112">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3113">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3113">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3114">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3114">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3115">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3115">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3116">**Data_Doc_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3116">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3119">**Data_Doc_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3119">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesavesaveassavefile"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3165">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3165">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3166">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word saglabā dokumentu jaunā dokumentā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3166">This event indicates Office Word saves a document into a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3167">Tādējādi Microsoft var noteikt darbības “saglabāt kā” kļūdas, kam ir būtiska nozīme, lai novērstu dokumenta datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3167">It allows Microsoft to detect errors in save-as which is important to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3168">Notikums pārrauga, vai dokumenta saglabāšana darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3168">The event monitors whether save-as is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3169">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3169">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3170">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3170">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3173">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā mērķa dokumentam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3173">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event for the destination document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3174">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3174">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3177">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3177">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordworddocumentdirtyflagchanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3290">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3290">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3291">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word rediģē dokumentu, kas dokumenta iekšējo stāvokli padara "netīru".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3291">This event indicates Office Word edits a document which changes the document internal state into "dirty".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3292">Tas ļauj Microsoft novērtēt dokumenta rediģēšanas līdzekļa darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3292">It allows Microsoft to evaluate the feature health of edit-document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3293">Notikums ir lietotāja veikto rediģējumu periodiskais kontrolziņojums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3293">The event is a heartbeat of user edits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3294">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3294">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3295">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3295">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3296">**Data\_CollectionTime —** notikuma laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3296">**Data\_CollectionTime-** Timestamp of the event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3297">**Data\_DocumentLocation —** dokumenta atrašanās vietas tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3297">**Data\_DocumentLocation-** type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3298">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails —** dokumenta atrašanās vietas apakštips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3298">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails-** Sub-type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3299">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled —** norāda, vai ir iespējota iespēja vienmēr saglabāt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3299">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled-** Indicates whether always-save was enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3300">**Data\_FirstEditTime —** pirmās rediģēšanas laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3300">**Data\_FirstEditTime-** Timestamp of first edit</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3301">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors —** līdzautoru skaits, kuri sesijā rediģē dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3301">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors-** Number of coauthors editing the document during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3302">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied —** dokumentā veikto rediģējumu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3302">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied-** Number of edits made to the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3303">**Data\_Pdod —** dokumenta identifikators Office Word procesā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3303">**Data\_Pdod-** Document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3304">**Data\_UrlHash —** dokumenta ceļa jaukšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3304">**Data\_UrlHash-** Hash of the document path</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidoffice16bootlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3447">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3447">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3448">Ir būtiski svarīgs, lai fiksētu lietojumprogrammas veiktspējas rādītāju attiecībā uz lietojumprogrammas atbildes laiku no sāknēšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3448">Critical to capture for app performance metric with respect to the response time of the app from the boot.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3449">Microsoft to izmanto, lai apkopotu laiku, kas ir nepieciešams lietojumprogrammai, lai atbildētu, kā arī, lai noteiktu scenārijus, kas varat ietekmēt sāknēšanas laiku WXP lietojumprogrammās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3449">Microsoft uses this to collect the time taken for the app to be responsive and also detect scenarios that may impact boot time in WXP apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3450">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3450">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3451">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** — lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas atbildes laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3451">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** - App launch responsive time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3452">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** — būla, kas norāda, vai lietotne tika aizturēta sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3452">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3453">**CollectionTime** — notikuma laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3453">**CollectionTime** - Timestamp of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3454">**FileActivationAttempted** — būla, kas norāda, vai notika faila aktivizēšanas mēģinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3454">**FileActivationAttempted** - Boolean to indicate if file activation as attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3455">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** — lietojumprogrammas pavediena dīkstāves laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3455">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** - App thread idle time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3456">**IsThisFirstLaunch** — būla, kas norāda, vai lietojumprogrammu tiek sāknēta pirmo reizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3456">**IsThisFirstLaunch** - Boolean to indicate if this is first time app launch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3457">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** — būla, kas norāda, vai notika lietotāja interfeisa bloķēšana sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3457">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if there was a blocking UI during boot</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityofficejsappactivated"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3458">Office.Extensibility.OfficeJS.Appactivated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3458">Office.Extensibility.OfficeJS.Appactivated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3459">Ieraksta informāciju par neparedzētu Office izslēgšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3459">Records information about unexpected shutdowns of Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3460">Tas ļauj mums noteikt produkta avārijas vai, ja tas pārstāj reaģēt, un atrisināt šīs problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3460">This allows us to identify crashes or hangs in the product so that they can be addressed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3462">\*\*Data\_AirspaceInitTime:integer — \*\* Airspace Office komponentes inicializācijai veltītais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3462">**Data\_AirspaceInitTime:integer-** time taken to initialize Airspace office component</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3464">**Data\_APIInitTime:integer —** laiks, lai inicializētu Visio API moduli</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3464">**Data\_APIInitTime:integer -** time taken to initialize Visio API module</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3465">**Data\_AppSizeHeight —** pievienojumprogrammas**-** loga augstums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3465">**Data\_AppSizeHeight –** Add**-** in window size’s height</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3466">**Data\_AppSizeWidth —** pievienojumprogrammas**-** loga platums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3466">**Data\_AppSizeWidth –** Add**-** in window size’s width</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3467">**Data\_AppURL —** pievienojumprogrammas URL; reģistrē pilnu URL krātuves pievienojumprogrammām un URL domēnu pievienojumprogrammām, kas nav krātuves pievienojumprogrammas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3467">**Data\_AppURL -** URL of the Add in; Logs full URL for Store Add ins and URL domain for non-store Add ins</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3468">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3468">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3469">**Data\_AuthorsCount:integer —** autoru skaits, kuri rediģēja dokumentu šajā sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3469">**Data\_AuthorsCount:integer -** number of authors who edited the document in this session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3470">**Data\_BackgroundPages:integer —** fona lapu skaits shēmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3470">**Data\_BackgroundPages:integer -** number of background pages in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3471">**Data\_BootTime:integer —** Visio palaišanai nepieciešamais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3471">**Data\_BootTime:integer -** The amount of time it took to boot Visio</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3472">**Data\_Browser —** pārlūkprogrammas virkne ar informāciju par pārlūkprogrammu, piemēram, tips un versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3472">**Data\_Browser -** Browser string with information about the browser such as type, version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3473">**Data\_ChildWindowMixedModeTime:integer —** laiks, kas nepieciešams jauktā režīma iespējošanai programmā Visio (atvasinātajam logam var būt atšķirīgs DpiAwareness no primārā loga)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3473">**Data\_ChildWindowMixedModeTime:integer -** time taken to enable mixed mode in Visio (Child window can have different DpiAwareness from parent window)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3474">**Data\_CommentsCount:integer —** komentāru skaits dokumentā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3474">**Data\_CommentsCount:integer -** number of comments in document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3475">**Data\_ConnectionCount:integer —** datu savienojumu skaits shēmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3475">**Data\_ConnectionCount:integer -** number of data connection in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3476">**Data\_ContentMgrInitTim:integer —** laiks, kas nepieciešams satura pārvaldnieka inicializēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3476">**Data\_ContentMgrInitTim:integer -** time taken to initialize content manager</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3477">**Data\_CreateMainFrameTime:integer —** lieldatora laika izveide</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3477">**Data\_CreateMainFrameTime:integer -** Create mainframe time</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationhanging"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3618">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3618">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3619">Apkopo gadījumus, kad Office programmas palaišana aizņem neparedzēti daudz laika (> 5 sek.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3619">Collects when an Office add-in takes unexpectedly long to launch (>5 sec).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3620">Izmanto, lai atklātu un novērstu problēmas ar Office pievienojumprogrammu palaišanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3620">Used to detect and fix problems with Office add-ins launching.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3621">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3621">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3622">**AppId** — lietojumprogrammas ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3622">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3623">**AppInfo** — dati par pievienojumprogrammas veidu (uzdevumrūts vai UILess, vai iegulšanas utt.) un nodrošinātāja veidu (omen, SharePoint, filesystem utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3623">**AppInfo** - data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3624">**AppInstanceId** — lietojumprogrammas instances ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3624">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3625">**AssetId** — lietojumprogrammas līdzekļa ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3625">**AssetId** - asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3626">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** — aktivēto pievienojumprogrammu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3626">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3627">**RemoterType** — norāda pievienojumprogrammas aktivēšanai izmantotā attālinātāja veidu (uzticams, neuzticams, Win32webView, uzticams UDF utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3627">**RemoterType** - specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3628">**StoreType** — lietojumprogrammas izcelsme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3628">**StoreType** - origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3629">**TimeForAuth** — autentifikācijai iztērētais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3629">**TimeForAuth** - time spent on auth</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3630">**TimeForSandbox** — smilškastei iztērētais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3630">**TimeForSandbox** - time spent on the sandbox</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptdesktopbootime"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3885">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3885">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3886">Apkopo, kā tiek startēts PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3886">Collecting how PowerPoint is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3887">Iekļauta PowerPoint startēšana aizsargātā skatā, asistētas lasīšanas režīmā, no makro, drukāšana, jauns un tukšs dokuments, dokumenta atkopšana, no automatizācijas un, ja tas ir “Click-to-Run”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3887">It includes boot PowerPoint in protected view, in assisted reading mode, from Macro, print, new and blank document, document recovery, from automation and if it is click- to-run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3888">Tas apkopo arī PowerPoint startēšanas laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3888">It also collects how long it takes PowerPoint to boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3889">Šie dati ir kritiski svarīgi, lai nodrošinātu PowerPoint sekmīgu startēšanu no dažādiem režīmiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3889">This data is critical to guarantee PowerPoint performs well when booted from different modes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3890">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai fiksētu ilgu startēšanas laiku, atverot PowerPoint no dažādiem režīmiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3890">Microsoft uses this data to catch long booting time when opening PowerPoint from different modes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3891">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3891">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3892">**AssistedReading —** asistētas lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3892">**AssistedReading -** in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3893">**Automation —** no automatizācijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3893">**Automation -** from automation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3894">**Benchmark —** palaist izpildes kritēriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3894">**Benchmark -** run performance benchmark</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3895">**Blank —** tukšs dokuments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3895">**Blank -** blank document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3896">**BootTime —** sesijas startēšanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3896">**BootTime -** session boot time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3897">**Embedding —** dokumenta iegulšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3897">**Embedding -** embedding document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3898">**IsC2R —** ir “Click-to-Run”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3898">**IsC2R -** is click-to-run</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3899">**IsNew —** jauns dokuments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3899">**IsNew -** new document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3900">**IsOpen —** ir atvērts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3900">**IsOpen -** is open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3901">**Macro1 —** palaist makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3901">**Macro1 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3902">**Macro2 —** palaist makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3902">**Macro2 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3903">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** — komandrindā ir nestandarta atstarpe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3903">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – there is non-standard space in command line</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3904">**Print —** drukāt dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3904">**Print -** print document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3905">**PrintDialog —** drukāt dokumentu ar dialoglodziņu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3905">**PrintDialog -** print document with dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3906">**PrintPrinter —** drukāt dokumentu ar printeri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3906">**PrintPrinter -** print document with printer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3907">**ProtectedView —** aizsargātā skatā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3907">**ProtectedView -** in protected view</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3908">**Regserver —** reģistrēt PowerPoint kā COM serveri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3908">**Regserver -** Register PowerPoint as a COM server</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3909">**Restore —** atjaunot dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3909">**Restore -** restore document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3910">**Show —** rādīt dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3910">**Show -** show document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3911">**Time —** sesijas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3911">**Time -** session time</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3919">Project tiek startēta, atverot failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3919">Project is booted by opening a file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3920">Šis notikums norāda, ka lietotājs ir atvēris Office Project ar saistīto failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3920">This event indicates that a user has opened Office Project with an associated file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3921">Tas satur kritiski svarīgus datus, lai varētu startēt Project un ielādēt failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3921">It contains critical success data of making sure Project can start and load a file.</span></span>
