  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3923">**Data\_AlertTime —** laika periods, kad bija aktīvs startēšanas dialoglodziņš.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3923">**Data\_AlertTime -** The amount of time the boot dialog was active.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3924">**Data\_BootTime —** Project palaišanai nepieciešamais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3924">**Data\_BootTime -** The amount of time it took to boot Project</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3925">**Data\_CacheFileSize —** ja fails tika saglabāts kešatmiņā, faila lielums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3925">**Data\_CacheFileSize -** If the file was cached, the size of the file</span></span>

#### <a name="officesessionidproviderofficeprocesssessionstart"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-3958">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3958">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3959">Attiecas uz visām Office Windows lietojumprogrammām: win32 un UWP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3959">Applicable to all the Office windows-based applications: win32 and UWP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3960">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3960">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3961">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** nosūta pamatinformāciju jaunas Office sesijas sākumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3961">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** sends basic information upon the start of a new Office session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3962">To izmanto, lai saskaitītu unikālās sesijas, kas redzamas konkrētajā ierīcē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3962">This is used to count the number of unique sessions seen on a given device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3963">Tas tiek izmantots kā periodiska kontrolziņojuma notikums, lai pārliecinātos, vai lietojumprogramma darbojas ierīcē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3963">This is used as a heartbeat event to ensure that the application is running on a device or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3964">Turklāt to var izmantot kā kritiski svarīgu signālu par kopējo lietojumprogrammu uzticamību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3964">In addition, it serves as a critical signal for overall application reliability</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3965">**AppSessionGuid** — tās attiecīgās lietojumprogrammas sesijas identifikators, kuras sākums ir procesa izveides laiks un kas ilgst līdz procesa beigām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3965">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3966">Tas ir formatēts kā standarta 128 bitu GUID, ko veido četras daļas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3966">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3967">Šo četru daļu secība ir: (1) 32 bitu procesa ID (2) 16 bitu sesijas ID (3) 16 bitu palaišanas ID (4) 64 bitu procesa izveides laiks: UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3967">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3968">**processSessionId** — nejauši ģenerēts GUID, lai noteiktu programmas sesiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3968">**processSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3969">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** — konstanta Būla vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3969">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3970">Vienmēr patiess.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3970">Always true.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-3972">Norāda, ka pašreizējā Office sesija ir nodošanas sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3972">Indicates that the current Office session is a handoff session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-3973">Tas nozīmē, ka darbs ar lietotāja pieprasījumu, lai atvērtu dokumentu, tiek pārsūtīts uz jau darbojošos instanci tajā pašā programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-3973">This means that handling of a user’s request to open a document is being handed off to an already running instance of the same application.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopencmdfilemrupriv"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4008">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4008">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4009">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu no pēdējo lietoto dokumentu saraksta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4009">This event indicates Office Word opens a document from the Most Recent Used (MRU) list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4010">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4010">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4011">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana no pēdējo lietoto dokumentu saraksta darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4011">The event monitors whether fileopen-from-MRU is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4012">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4012">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4013">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4013">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4014">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4014">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4015">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4015">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4016">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4016">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4017">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4017">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4018">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4018">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenffileopenxstzcore"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4075">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4075">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4076">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu, uz kura lietotājs veic dubultklikšķi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4076">This event indicates Office Word opens a document who is double clicked by a user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4077">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4077">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4078">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana ar dubultklikšķi darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4078">The event monitors whether file-openfrom-file-double-click is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4079">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4079">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4080">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4080">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4081">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4081">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4082">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4082">Used for data quality diagnostics</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4083">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4083">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4084">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4084">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4085">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4085">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4086">**Data_BytesUnknown**— baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4086">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4087">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4087">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4088">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4088">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4089">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4089">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4090">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4090">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenifrinitargs"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4142">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4142">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4143">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu, izmantojot COM aktivizēšanu vai komandrindu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4143">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via COM activation or command line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4144">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4144">It also contains critical file open performance data, and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4145">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana no komandrindas darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4145">The event monitors whether file-open-from-command-line is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4146">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4146">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4147">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4147">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4148">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes —** norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4148">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes -** Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4149">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4149">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4150">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous —** baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4150">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4151">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork —** baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4151">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4152">**Data\_BytesSynchronous —** baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4152">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4153">**Data\_BytesUnknown —** baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4153">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4154">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4154">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4155">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4155">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4156">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4156">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4157">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4157">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4158">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4158">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4159">**Data\_Doc\_Ext —** dokumentu paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4159">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4160">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4160">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4161">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4161">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenloadfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4208">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4208">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4209">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu, izmantojot atvēršanas dialoglodziņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4209">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via Open dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4210">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4210">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4211">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana no atvēršanas dialoglodziņa darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4211">The event monitors whether file-open-from-the-open-filedialog is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4212">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4212">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4213">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4213">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4214">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4214">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4215">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4215">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4216">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4216">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4217">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4217">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4218">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4218">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4219">**Data_BytesUnknown**— baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4219">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4220">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4220">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4221">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4221">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4222">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4222">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4223">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4223">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4224">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4224">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4225">**Data_Doc_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4225">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4226">**Data_Doc_Ext —** dokumenta paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4226">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4227">**Data_Doc_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4227">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4228">**Data_Doc_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4228">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4229">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash —** klientu identificējama domēna nosaukuma vienvirziena jaukšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4229">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4230">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId —** tādas lietotāja identitātes vienvirziena jaukšana, kas tiek izmantota atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4230">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4231">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario —** dokumenta atvēršanas ieraksti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4231">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4232">**Data_Doc_IOFlags —** atskaites par kešotajiem karodziņiem, kas tiek izmantoti atvēršanas pieprasījuma opciju iestatīšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4232">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4233">**Data_Doc_IrmRights —** dokumentam/lietotājam piemērotās elektronisko datu politikas atļautās darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4233">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4234">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4234">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4235">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments tiek atbalstīts sadarbības pakalpojumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4235">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4378">**Data\_ParagraphCount —** rindkopu skaits dokumentā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4378">**Data\_ParagraphCount -** paragraph count of the document</span></span>

#### <a name="officeintelligentserviceprivacyconsentprivacyevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4389">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4389">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4390">Šis notikums apzīmē lietotāja vai sistēmas iniciētu darbību, kas ir daļa no Office lietotāju pieredzes ar konfidencialitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4390">This event represents a user or system initiated action that is part of the privacy User experience for Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4391">Tas tiek aktivizēts konfidencialitātes dialogos Pirmā palaišana, dialogā Konta konfidencialitāte un konfidencialitātes paziņojumos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4391">It is triggered on the privacy First Run dialogs, Account Privacy dialog, and privacy notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4392">Notikums tiek izmantots, lai izprastu šādus faktorus: lietotāju piekrišana Office konfidencialitātes iestatījumiem, lietotāju veiktas Office konfidencialitātes iestatījumu izmaiņas un Office konfidencialitātes iestatījumu atjaunināšana lietotāju sesijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4392">The event is used to understand the following: users consenting to Office privacy settings, users changing Office privacy settings, and Office privacy settings getting updated in user sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4393">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4393">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4394">**Data_ActionId —** lietotāja darbība konfidencialitātes dialogā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4394">**Data_ActionId -** User action in a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4395">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState —** lietotāju politikas iestatījums papildu savienotajām pieredzēm pēc izvēles</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4395">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState -** User policy setting for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4396">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState —** lietotāja iestatījums lejupielādētajam saturam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4396">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for downloaded content</span></span> 
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4397">**Data_ForwardLinkId —** saite uz konfidencialitātes dokumentiem saistībā ar lietotāja scenāriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4397">**Data_ForwardLinkId -** Link to privacy documentation for the user scenario</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4398">**Data_HRESULT —** kļūdu ieraksts mijiedarbības laikā ar konfidencialitātes dialogu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4398">**Data_HRESULT -** Record of errors during interaction with a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4399">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser —** lietotāja licences kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4399">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser -** User license category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4400">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState —** lietotāja iestatījums savienotajiem pakalpojumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4400">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState -** User setting for connected services</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4401">**Data_RecordRegistry —** uzņēmumu konfidencialitātes dialoga rādīšanas ieraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4401">**Data_RecordRegistry -** Record of showing the enterprise privacy dialog</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappdomainunhandledexceptionhandlerfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4417">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4417">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4418">Apkopo informāciju par neapstrādātiem izņēmumiem, izmantojot programmu Data Streamer.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4418">Collects information for any unhandled exceptions using the Data Streamer App.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4419">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai pārraudzītu programmas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4419">This data is used to monitor the health of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4420">Šo notikumu ģenerē Microsoft Data Streamer Excel pievienojumprogrammai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4420">This event is generated by Microsoft Data Streamer for Excel Add-in.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4421">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4421">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4422">**Exception** — izņēmuma izsaukuma steks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4422">**Exception** - Call stack for the Exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4423">**Event Name** — notikuma nosaukums ir notikuma kategorija un notikuma etiķete.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4423">**Event Name** - Event Name is the Event Category and Event Label.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_identitydomainname"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4424">Office_Apple_IdentityDomainName</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4424">Office_Apple_IdentityDomainName</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4425">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4425">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4426">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu mūsu sistēmas darbspēju, kā arī noteiktu domēna lietotāju neveiksmes iemeslus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4426">The event is used to monitor the health of our system as well as investigating causes of failures by certain domain users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4427">Mēs apkopojam domēnu, ko izmanto mūsu lietotāji autentificēšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4427">We collect the domain used by our users when they authenticate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4428">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai palīdzētu noteikt un novērst problēmas, kas var neradīt pārāk lielu iespaidu plašākā līmenī, bet ir ļoti iespaidīgas noteiktiem lietotāju domēniem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4428">We use this data to help identify and fix those issues that might not seem too impactful at a broader level, but that turn out to be very impactful to a certain domain of users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4429">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4429">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4430">**Data_Domain** — autentifikācijai izmantotais domēns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4430">**Data_Domain** - the domain used for authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4431">**Data_IdentityProvider** — autentifikācijas identitātes nodrošinātāja nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4431">**Data_IdentityProvider** - The authentication identity provider name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4432">(piem., LiveId vai ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4432">(i.e. LiveId or ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4433">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** — autentifikācijas identitātes nodrošinātāja nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4433">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** - The authentication identity provider code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4434">(Skaitlis)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4434">(A number)</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_systemhealthappexitmacandios"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4435">Office_Apple_SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4435">Office_Apple_SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4436">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4436">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4437">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu mūsu Office programmu darbspēju, kā arī noteiktu kļūmju iemeslus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4437">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4438">Mēs apkopojam datus katras programmas iziešanas laikā, lai noteiktu, vai no programmas ir iziets bez aizķeršanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4438">We collect data on each application exit to determine whether an application exited gracefully.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4439">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4439">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4440">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** — sesijas identifikators, kas veic programmas iziešanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4440">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** - The identifier for the session that experience the application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4441">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** — tās programmas sekundārā versija, kurā tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4441">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4442">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** — sesijas ilgums no sākuma līdz beigām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4442">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** - The length of the session from start to exit</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4443">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** — telemetrijas darbspējas rādītājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4443">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4444">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** — telemetrijas darbspējas rādītājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4444">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4445">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** — tās operētājsistēmas lokalizācija, ar kuru tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4445">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** - The Locale of the OS under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4446">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** — tās operētājsistēmas lokalizācija, ar kuru tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4446">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** - The OS version under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4447">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** — rezidenta atmiņas apjoms, kas tika patērēts, kad tika veikta lietojumprogrammas iziešana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4447">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of resident memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4448">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** — identifikators, kas aprakstīs konkrētās kļūdas trāpījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4448">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** - An identifier that will denote the specific error being hit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4449">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** — laiks, kad sesija sākās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4449">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** - The time at which the session started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4450">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** — novērotais programmas iziešanas veids (ja tas bija ar aizķeršanos iziešanas gadījumā, šis kods apzīmēs novērotās kļūdas tipu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4450">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** - The type of application exit observed (if it was an ungraceful exit, this code will denote the type of error observed)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4451">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** — programmas galvenā versija, kurā tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4451">**Data_AffectedSessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4452">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** — virtuālās atmiņas apjoms, kas tika patērēts, kad notika programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4452">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of virtual memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4453">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** — vai programmas iziešana bija bez aizķeršanās vai ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4453">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** - Whether the application Exit was graceful or ungraceful.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4455">Šis notikums tiek ģenerēts, kad Office lietotāju versijā notiek COM pievienojumprogrammas avārija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4455">Event generated when COM Add-in crashes on a consumer version of Office applications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4460">**Method** — Office metode, kurā radās izņēmums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4460">**Method** – Office method where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4462">**AddinId** — pievienojumprogrammas klases ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4462">**AddinId** – the add-in Class Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4463">**AddinProgId** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4463">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4465">**AddinTimeDateStamp** — pievienojumprogrammas laikspiedols no DLL metadatiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4465">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4466">**AddinVersion** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4466">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4467">**AddinFileName** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4467">**AddinFileName** – deprecated</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4487">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4487">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4497">**ErrorCodeime** — iztērētais laiks kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4497">**ErrorCode** - Total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4498">**IsDebug** - norāda, vai sesija ir atkļūdošanas sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4498">**IsDebug** - indicates if session is a debug session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4499">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** — aktivēto pievienojumprogrammu skaitītājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4499">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - Counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4500">**RemoterType** — norāda pievienojumprogrammas aktivēšanai izmantotā attālinātāja veidu (uzticams, neuzticams, Win32webView, uzticams UDF utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4500">**RemoterType** - Specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF, etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4501">**StoreType** — lietojumprogrammas izcelsme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4501">**StoreType** - Origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4502">**Atzīme**— norāda, kur tieši kodam radās kļūme, izmantojot ar to saistīto unikālo atzīmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4502">**Tag**- Specifies where exactly the code has failed using the unique tag associated with it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4503">**UsesSharedRuntime** — norāda, ka programma izmanto sharedRuntime vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4503">**UsesSharedRuntime** - indicates the app uses sharedRuntime or not.</span></span>

### <a name="application-feature-performance-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4668">*Lietojumprogrammas līdzekļu izpildes apakštips*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4668">*Application feature performance subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4669">Slikts atbildes laiks vai slikta veiktspēja tādos scenārijos kā programmas startēšana vai faila atvēršana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4669">Poor response time or performance for scenarios such as application start up or opening a file.</span></span>

#### <a name="initial_page_landing"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4670">Initial_page_landing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4670">Initial_page_landing</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4671">Šis pasākums palīdz izsekot, kāda veida pieredze lietotājiem tiek rādīta, kad tie nonāk mūsu programmas lapā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4671">This event helps track the type of experience that users see when they land in our application page.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4672">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai noteiktu lietotāju plūsmu katrā programmas lietošanas pieredzē, kā arī palīdz mums viegli konsolidēt eksperimentu rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4672">This data is used to determine the traffic of users piped into each experience in our application and also helps us to easily consolidate experimentation results.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4673">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4673">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4674">**Lapa** — tā tiek lietota, lai izsekotu, kāda veida pieredzi lietotājs pirmo reizi redz, kad nonāk lapā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4674">**Page** - This is used to track the type of experience that user first sees when they land on our page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4675">Iespējamās vērtības ir "Izmēģinājumversija", "izlaist", "Salikts", "Abonements" utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4675">Possible values are “Trial”, “Skip”, “Prebundled”, “Subscription” etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4676">**storeExperience** — var izmantot, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir tiesīgs skatīt veikala SDK pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4676">**storeExperience** - This is used to determine if user was eligible to see the Store SDK Experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4677">**stringVariant** — var izmantot, lai noteiktu, kāda veida virknes lietotājs redz, kad nonāk lapā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4677">**stringVariant** - This is used to determine the type of strings that user sees when they land on our page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4678">Ņemiet vērā, ka jebkurai lapai, piemēram, "Izmēģinājumversija", lietotājs var būt tiesīgs skatīt dažādas virknes atkarībā no tā, vai viņiem ir instalēta mantota sistēma Office vai ja lietotājs iepriekš aktivizēja sistēmu Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4678">Note that for any page such as “Trial”, user can be eligible to see different strings based on whether they had Legacy Office installed, or if they had previously activated Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4679">Iespējamie šī rekvizīta uzskaitījumi ir "LegacyUpsell", "OfficeOpened", "Noklusējums", "YesIntent", "NoIntent" utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4679">Possible enumerations of this property are “LegacyUpsell”, “OfficeOpened”, “Default”, “YesIntent”, “NoIntent” etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4680">**windowsBuildType** — var izmantot, lai izsekotu WindowsBuildType, ko lietotājs ir ieplānojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4680">**windowsBuildType** - This is used to track the type of WindowsBuildType that user is on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4681">t.i., "RS4", "RS5", "RS19H1", "Vibranium" u.c. Tā kā mūsu pieredze parasti ir vērsta uz dažādiem WindowsBuildTypes, šis rekvizīts ir svarīgs, lai atšķirtu ieviešanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4681">i.e. “RS4”, “RS5”, “RS19H1”, “Vibranium etc. As our experiences are usually targeted to different WindowsBuildTypes, this property is vital in differentiating between rollouts.</span></span> 

#### <a name="ipcpbootstrapuser"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4682">IpcpBootstrapUser</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4682">IpcpBootstrapUser</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4688">**AppInfo.Version** — lietojumprogrammas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4688">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4689">**iKey** — pieteikšanās pakalpojuma servera ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4689">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4690">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko nodrošina lietojumprogramma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4690">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4691">**RMS.AuthCallbackProvided** — norāda, vai autentificēšanas atzvanīšana tiek nodrošināta kā API izsaukuma ievade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4691">**RMS.AuthCallbackProvided** - Indicate if provides the authentication callback as input of the API call or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4692">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.ExtranetUrl** — ārtīkla savienojuma informācijas vietrādis URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4692">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.ExtranetUrl** - the extranet URL in connection info</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4693">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.IntranetUrl** — iekštīkla savienojuma informācijas vietrādis URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4693">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.IntranetUrl** - the intranet URL in connection info</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4694">**RMS.ConnectionMode** — savienojuma režīms starp tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klientu un serveri: tiešsaistē vai bezsaistē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4694">**RMS.ConnectionMode** - The connection mode between Rights Management Service client and server: online or offline</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4695">**RMS.Duration** — kopējais laiks API izsaukuma veikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4695">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for API call to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4696">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** — kopējais patērētais laiks mīnus ārējās operācijas, piemēram, tīkla latentums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4696">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4697">**RMS.ErrorCode** — atgrieztais kļūdas kods, ja tāds ir, no API izsaukuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4697">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4698">**RMS.GuestTenant** — lietotāja viesa nomnieka ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4698">**RMS.GuestTenant** - Guest tenant Id for the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4700">**RMS.HttpCall** — norāda, vai ir HTTP operācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4700">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4701">**RMS.Identity.ExtranetUrl** — lietotāja tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera ārtīkla URL, kas tiek apkopots, iegūstot jaunu tiesību konta sertifikātu no servera</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4701">**RMS.Identity.ExtranetUrl** - The extranet URL of Rights Management service server for the user, collected while getting a new Rights Account Certificate from the server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4702">**RMS.Identity.IntranetUrl** — lietotāja tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera iekštīkla URL, kas tiek apkopots, iegūstot jaunu tiesību konta sertifikātu no servera</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4702">**RMS.Identity.IntranetUrl** - The intranet URL of Rights Management service server for the user, collected while getting a new Rights Account Certificate from the server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4703">**RMS.Identity.Status** — pirmā reize, lai iegūtu tiesību konta sertifikātu no servera vai atjaunotu tiesību konta sertifikātu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4703">**RMS.Identity.Status** - The first time to get Rights Account Certificate from the server or renew the Rights Account Certificate</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4704">**RMS.Identity.Type** — lietotāja konta tips, piemēram, Windows konts vai Live konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4704">**RMS.Identity.Type** - The type of the user account such as windows account or live account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4705">**RMS.Identity.UserProvided** — norāda, vai lietotāja e-pasta adrese ir nodrošināta, kad saņemat jaunu tiesību konta sertifikātu no servera</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4705">**RMS.Identity.UserProvided** - Indicate if the user email address provided or not while getting new Rights Account Certificate from the server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4706">**RMS.IssuerId** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera ID, kas izsniedz tiesību konta sertifikātu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4706">**RMS.IssuerId** - The Id of the Rights Management Service server which issues Rights Account Certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4709">**RMS.Result** — API izsaukums sekmīgs vai neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4709">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4710">**RMS.ScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko definē API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4710">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4712">**RMS.ServerType** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4712">**RMS.ServerType** - The type of Rights Management Service Server</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficelaunchtolandingpagelatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4723">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeLaunchToLandingPageLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4723">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeLaunchToLandingPageLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4724">Ir būtiski svarīgs, lai fiksētu lietojumprogrammas veiktspējas rādītāju attiecībā uz lietojumprogrammas atbildes laiku no sāknēšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4724">Critical to capture for app performance metric with respect to the response time of the app from the boot.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4725">Microsoft to izmanto, lai apkopotu laiku, kas ir nepieciešams lietojumprogrammai, lai atbildētu, kā arī, lai noteiktu scenārijus, kas varat ietekmēt sāknēšanas laiku WXP lietojumprogrammās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4725">Microsoft uses this to collect the time taken for the app to be responsive and also detect scenarios that may impact boot time in WXP apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4726">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4726">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4727">**AnyCrashInteractionDuringBoot** — būla jebkurai avārijai, kas rodas sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4727">**AnyCrashInteractionDuringBoot** - Boolean for any crash encountered during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4728">**AppActivationTimeInMs** — lietojumprogrammas fāzes laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4728">**AppActivationTimeInMs** - App phase time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4729">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** — būla lietojumprogrammas atlikšanai sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4729">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean for app suspension during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4730">**AvailableMemoryInMB** — pieejamā atmiņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4730">**AvailableMemoryInMB** - available memory</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4731">**CollectionTime** — notikuma laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4731">**CollectionTime** - Timestamp of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4732">**DalvikHeapLimitInMB** — kaudzes informācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4732">**DalvikHeapLimitInMB** - Heap info</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4733">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** — būla, kas norāda, vai dokuments ir atgūts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4733">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Boolean to indicate if any document was recovered</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4734">**ExtractionDone** — vietējās bibliotēkas izvilkšanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4734">**ExtractionDone** - Native library extraction time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4735">**FastBootGainTimeInMs** — ātrās sāknēšanas pabeigšanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4735">**FastBootGainTimeInMs** - Time for fast boot completion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4736">**FileActivationAttempted** — būla, kas norāda, vai lietojumprogramma tika palaista faila aktivācijas dēļ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4736">**FileActivationAttempted** - Boolean to indicate if app was launched due to File activation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4737">**HasLogcatLoggingImpactOnBoot** — būla, kas norāda, vai logcat rīks ietekmēja sāknēšanas laiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4737">**HasLogcatLoggingImpactOnBoot** - Boolean to indicate if logcat impacted boot time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4738">**IsThisFirstLaunch** — būla, kas norāda, vai tā ir pirmā lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas reize</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4738">**IsThisFirstLaunch** - Boolean to indicate if this is first app launch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4739">**LatencyTimeInMilliSec** — latentums milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4739">**LatencyTimeInMilliSec** - latency in milli second</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4740">**LibrarySharingTimeInMs** — bibliotēku koplietošanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4740">**LibrarySharingTimeInMs** - time for sharing libraries</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4741">**LoadMinLibsTimeInMs** — minimālās bibliotēku kopas ielādes laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4741">**LoadMinLibsTimeInMs** - Loading time for the minimum set of libraries</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4742">**MruListingTimeInMs** — MRU ielādes laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4742">**MruListingTimeInMs** - time to load MRU</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4743">**NativeLibrariesLoadTime** — CPP bibliotēkas ielādes laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4743">**NativeLibrariesLoadTime** - CPP library load time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4744">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** — darbībā esošu procesu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4744">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** - number of running processes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4745">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** — darbībā esošu procesu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4745">**NumberOfRunningProcesses** - Number of running processes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4746">**NumberOfRunningServices** — darbībā esošo pakalpojumu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4746">**NumberOfRunningServices** - Number of running services</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4747">**OfficeActivityTimeInMs** — OfficeActivity inicializācijas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4747">**OfficeActivityTimeInMs** - Time for initing OfficeActivity</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_msoappdelegate_bootperf"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4841">Office_Apple_MsoAppDelegate_BootPerf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4841">Office_Apple_MsoAppDelegate_BootPerf</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4842">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4842">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4843">Pasākums tiek izmantots, lai apkopotu laiku un patērēto atmiņu, izmantojot Office programmas, kā arī detalizētu informāciju par to, kāda veida sāknēšana ir pabeigta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4843">The event is used to collect time and memory consumed during boot by Office apps, as well as some details on the type of boot done.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4844">Šis notikums palīdz mums uzraudzīt mūsu sniegumu un nodrošināt veiktspējas uzlabojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4844">This event helps us monitor our performance and provide performance improvements.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4847">**Data_AppLaunchFinishSystemTime** — laikspiedols konkrētajā sāknēšanas koda marķierī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4847">**Data_AppLaunchFinishSystemTime** - A timestamp at a particular boot code marker</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4848">**Data_AppLaunchStartSystemTime** — laikspiedols konkrētajā sāknēšanas koda marķierī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4848">**Data_AppLaunchStartSystemTime** - A timestamp at a particular boot code marker</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4849">**Data_ResidentMemory** — pieejamās rezidenta atmiņas momentuzņēmums sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4849">**Data_ResidentMemory** - A snapshot of the available resident memory during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4850">**Data_VirtualMemory** — pieejamās virtuālās atmiņas momentuzņēmums sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4850">**Data_VirtualMemory** - A snapshot of the available virtual memory during boot</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_ungracefulappexithangsinprevioussession"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4851">Office_Apple_UngracefulAppExitHangsInPreviousSession</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4851">Office_Apple_UngracefulAppExitHangsInPreviousSession</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4852">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4852">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4853">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu mūsu Office programmu darbspēju, kā arī noteiktu kļūmju iemeslus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4853">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4854">Mēs apkopojam, cik reizes programma izrādījās nereaģējoša pirms iziešanas no programmas ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4854">We collect the number of times an application appeared to be unresponsive prior to hitting an ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4855">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4855">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4856">**Data_HangsDetected** — cik reizes programma izrādījās nereaģējoša pirms iziešanas no programmas ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4856">**Data_HangsDetected** - The number of times the application appeared to become unresponsive prior to observing the ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4857">**Data_LastSessionId** — tās sesijas identifikators, kurā tika novērota iziešana no programmas ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4857">**Data_LastSessionId** - The identifier for the session in which the ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4858">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** — tās programmas sekundārā versija, kurā tika novērota iziešana no programmas ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4858">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4859">**Data_SessionVersion** — programmas galvenā versija, kurā tika novērota iziešana no programmas ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4859">**Data_SessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_whatsnewerrorandwarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4860">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4860">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4861">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4861">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4862">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu, kas ir jaunā līdzekļa darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4862">The event is used to monitor the health of the What’s New feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4863">Šis notikums norāda, ka, parsējot jaunumu saturu, radās kļūda/brīdinājums, norādot uz potenciālām satura autorēšanas problēmām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4863">This event denotes that an error/warning occurred while parsing What's New content, pointing to potential content authoring issues.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4864">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4864">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4865">**Data_ContentKey** — rādītājs uz satura sadaļu, kas visticamāk izraisīja kļūdu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4865">**Data_ContentKey** - A pointer to the section of the content that is likely to have caused the error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4866">**Data_ErrorCode** — novērotais kļūdas kods (ja pieejams)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4866">**Data_ErrorCode** - The observed error code (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4867">**Data_ErrorDescription** — kļūdas apraksts (ja pieejams)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4867">**Data_ErrorDescription** - A description of the error (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4868">**Data_EventID** — mēs apkopojam virkni, kas norāda novērotās kļūdas tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4868">**Data_EventID** - We collect a string representing the type of error observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4869">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** — vai saturā ir bagātināts html</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4869">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** - Whether the content contains rich html</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4870">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** — vai saturā ir vienumu hierarhija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4870">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** - Whether the content contains a hierarchy of items</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4871">**Data_LengthOfRawData** — satura lielums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4871">**Data_LengthOfRawData** - The size of the content</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4872">**Data_RequestURL** — vietrādis URL, no kura saturs tika lejupielādēts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4872">**Data_RequestURL** - The URL from which the content was downloaded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4873">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** — valoda, kurā bija saturs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4873">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** - The language the content was in.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4874">**Data_StatusCode** — kļūdas statuss (ja pieejams)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4874">**Data_StatusCode** - The status of the error (if available)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityrichapimethodinvocation"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4875">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4875">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4876">Šis notikums aktivizējas, kad klients izmanto Office pievienojumprogrammu un sazinās ar Rich API pakalpojuma sniegšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4876">When customer uses an Office Add-in and calls Rich API for providing service, this event will be triggered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4877">Izmanto, lai izmērītu pakalpojuma uzticamību, veiktspēju un lietojumu Rich API metodes izsaukšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4877">Used to measure the service reliability, performance and usage for Rich API method invocation.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4878">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4878">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4879">**API** — pilns API nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4879">**Api** - Full name of the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4880">**DispFlag** — bitu karodziņš, kas apraksta metodes izsaukuma tipu (piem., 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4880">**DispFlag** - A bit flag describing the type of method call (Ex: 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4881">**DispId** — izsauktās metodes izsūtīšanas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4881">**DispId** - Dispatch ID for the method being called</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4882">**HResult** — metodes izsaukšanas HResult.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4882">**HResult** - HResult for the method call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4883">**Latency** — izsaukuma latentums mikrosekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4883">**Latency** - Latency for the call, in microseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4884">**ReqId** — pakešu pieprasījuma GUID, pie kura pieder šī metode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4884">**ReqId** - GUID for the batch request that this method belongs to</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4885">**TypeId** — interfeisa GUID, uz kura šī metode tiek izsaukta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4885">**TypeId** - GUID for the interface on which this method being called</span></span>


#### <a name="officemanageabilityserviceapplypolicy"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4886">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4886">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4887">Kritiski svarīgi telemetrijas dati, lai izsekotu kļūmi\\Sekmīgi lietoti mākoņa politikas iestatījumi reģistrā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4887">Critical telemetry to track failure\\Success of applying cloud policy settings to registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4888">LastError norāda, kāpēc un kur neizdevās politikas lietošana reģistrā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4888">LastError tells why and where the Application of policy in registry failed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4890">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** — izņēmuma ziņojums politikas lietošanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4890">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** - The exception msg if any while policy was being applied</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4891">**Data.Cid** — dinamiski ģenerēts korelācijas identifikators, kas nosūtīts uz pakalpojumu, kad tika veikts pakalpojuma izsaukums, lai ienestu mākoņa politiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4891">**Data.Cid** - dynamically generated correlation identifier sent to the service when the service call was made to fetch the cloud policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4892">Tiek izmantots, lai korelētu, kurš izsaukums izraisīja problēmu, lietojot politikas mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4892">Used to correlate which call caused an issue while applying the policies on the cloud.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4893">**Data.Last Error** — viena no piecām virknes vērtībām (skaitītājiem), kas reģistrē, kurš politikas lietojums posms tika izpildīts, kad radās izņēmums </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4893">**Data.Last Error** - One of five string values (enumerators) to log which stage of policy application was being executed when the exception occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4903">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** — vai bija redzams dialoglodziņš Profila izvēle</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4903">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Whether the Choose Profile Dialog was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4907">**ShowSafeModeDlg** — vai sesija ir atvērta drošajā režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4907">**ShowSafeModeDlg** - is the session opened in safe mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4908">**ShowScanPstDlg** — krātuves labošanas pārbaude parādīja kļūdas ziņojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4908">**ShowScanPstDlg** - Store repair check displayed error message</span></span>
