- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4920">**EventType** — notikuma ar pasliktināto veiktspēju veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4920">**EventType** - type of event experiencing degraded performance</span></span>


#### <a name="officeperformanceboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4921">Office.Performance.Boot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4921">Office.Performance.Boot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4922">Tiek apkopots, palaižot Office programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4922">Collected when an Office application is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4923">Ietver informāciju par to, vai palaišana tika sākta, atverot failu vai palaižot no sākuma izvēlnes, vai tā bija pirmā programmas palaišana, cik daudz atmiņas programma izmanto un vai lietotājam tika rādīts bloķēšanas UI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4923">Includes whether the boot was initiated by opening a file or launching via the Start menu, whether this was the first boot of the application, how much memory the application is using, and whether there was any blocking UI shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4924">Tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu, cik ātri Office programmas tiek palaistas un cik daudz atmiņas tās izmanto, kad tiek startētas, lai nodrošinātu pieņemamu lietotāja pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4924">Used to measure how fast Office applications boot and how much memory they use when they start, to ensure there is an acceptable user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4925">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4925">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4926">**ActivationKind** — vai programma tika startēta, palaižot no sākuma izvēlnes, atverot failu vai izmantojot OLE automatizāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4926">**ActivationKind** - Whether the application was started by launching from the Start menu, by opening a file, or through OLE Automation.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4927">**BootToStart** — vai lietotājs ir izvēlējies sākuma ekrāna parādīšanu lietojumprogrammas startēšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4927">**BootToStart** - Whether the user has chosen to show the start screen when this application starts.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4928">**DocLocation** —  dokumenta atvēršanas brīdī norāda uz dokumenta izcelsmes pakalpojumu (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, u. tml.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4928">**DocLocation** -  When opening a document, indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4929">**FirstBoot** — vai šī bija pirmā programmas palaišana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4929">**FirstBoot** - Whether this was a first boot of the application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4930">**InitializationDuration** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai vispirms inicializētu Office procesu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4930">**InitializationDuration** - The duration in microseconds it took to first initialize the Office process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4931">**InterruptionMessageId** — vai palaišanu pārtrauca dialogs, pieprasot lietotāja ievadi, kā arī šī dialoga ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4931">**InterruptionMessageId** - If the boot was interrupted by a dialog asking for user input, the ID of the dialog.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4932">**TotalWorkingSetMB** — atmiņas apjoms megabaitos procesa darba kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4932">**TotalWorkingSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process’s working set.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4933">**VirtualSetMB** — atmiņas apjoms megabaitos procesa virtuālajā kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4933">**VirtualSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process’s virtual set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4934">(Tikai MacOS/iOS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4934">(MacOS / iOS only)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4935">**WorkingSetPeakMB** — vislielākais atmiņas apjoms megabaitos, kas līdz šim ir bijis procesa darba kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4935">**WorkingSetPeakMB** - The largest amount of memory in megabytes that was ever in the process’s working set so far.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4947">**Data_RegisterInsider** — Office Insider reģistrācijas statuss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4947">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4949">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** — pašreizējais reģistrācijas stāvoklis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4949">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsidershowofficeinsiderdlg"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4951">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4951">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4952">Kritiskais signāls, kas izseko lietotāja mijiedarbību ar dialoglogu Pievienojies programmai Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4952">Critical signal tracking user interaction with Join Office Insider dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4953">Tiek izmantots, lai identificētu jebkāda veida problēmas lietotāja iniciēto izmaiņu īstenošanā, piemēram, pievienošanās vai izstāšanās no Office Insider programmas un Office Insider līmeņa izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4953">It is used for identifying any issues in performing user-initiated changes such as joining or leaving Office Insider program and changing Office Insider level.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4954">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4954">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4955">**Data_AcceptedContactMeNew** — norāda, vai lietotājs, pievienojoties Office Insider programmai, ir piekritis saziņai ar Microsoft.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4955">**Data_AcceptedContactMeNew** - Indicates if a user has accepted to be contacted by Microsoft upon joining Office Insider program</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4956">**Data_InsiderLevel** — Insider līmenis, atverot dialoglogu “Pievienojies Office Insider”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4956">**Data_InsiderLevel** - Insider Level on opening of “Join Office Insider” dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4957">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** — Insider līmenis, aizverot dialoglogu “Pievienojies Office Insider”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4957">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** - Insider level on closing of “Join Office Insider” dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4958">**Data_IsInternalUser** — norāda, vai programma darbojas ar Microsoft korporatīvā konta akreditācijas datiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4958">**Data_IsInternalUser** - Indicates whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4959">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** — norāda, vai kods varēja noteikt to, vai programma darbojas ar Microsoft korporatīvā konta akreditācijas datiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4959">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** - Indicates whether the code could determine whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4960">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** — norāda, vai Office Insider biļetena abonēšanas saite tika aktivizēta pie nosacījuma, ka lietotājs pievienojās Office Insider programmai, biļetena abonementa funkcija ir iespējota un lietotājs nav atcēlis Office Insider biļetena abonementa tīmekļa vietnes atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4960">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** - Indicates whether Office Insider Newsletter Subscription link was triggered under condition that user has joined Office Insider program, Newsletter Subscription feature is enabled, and the user have not cancelled opening of Office Insider Newsletter Subscription webpage.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4961">**Data_RegisterInsider** — Office Insider reģistrācijas statuss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4961">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4962">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** — Office Insider reģistrācijas rezultāta kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4962">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4963">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** — pašreizējais reģistrācijas stāvoklis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4963">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4964">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** — pieprasītais reģistrācijas stāvoklis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4964">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** - Requested registration state</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisiofileopenreliability"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-4974">Office.Visio.VisioFileOpenReliability</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4974">Office.Visio.VisioFileOpenReliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-4975">Šis notikums apkopo failu atvēršanas izpildes datus par Visio Dev16.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4975">This event collects File open perf data for Visio Dev16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4976">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai pārraudzītu Visio Dev16 faila atvēršanas darbības izpildi, un saista to ar tādiem failu rekvizītiem kā faila lielums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4976">This event is used to monitor performance of File open and associates it with file properties like file size for Visio Dev16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4977">Faila rekvizīti sniedz mums iespēju ātrāk atkļūdot problēmas un uzzināt to cēloņus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4977">File properties enable us debug and root cause issues faster.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4979">\*\*Data\_CorrelationId: string — \*\*dokumentu korelācijas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4979">**Data\_CorrelationId: string -** Document correlation identifier</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4980">**Data\_DocIsEnterpriseProtected: bool —** patiess, ja dokuments ir aizsargāts, izmantojot Windows informācijas aizsardzību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4980">**Data\_DocIsEnterpriseProtected: bool -** true if document is protected with Windows information protection</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4981">**Data\_DocumentId: string —** faila ceļa GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4981">**Data\_DocumentId: string -** GUID of file path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4982">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds:double —** laiks milisekundēs, lai pabeigtu saglabāšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4982">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds: double -** Duration to complete save as in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4983">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double —** argumenta DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds kvadrāta vērtība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4983">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double -** squared value for DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4984">**Data\_ErrorCode: integer —** faila atvēršanas kļūmes iekšējas kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4984">**Data\_ErrorCode: integer -** Internal error code for file open failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4985">**Data\_Extension\_Docs: string —** atvērtas shēmas faila paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4985">**Data\_Extension\_Docs: string -** File extension of diagram opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4986">**Data\_FileIOBytesRead: int —** saglabāšanas laikā nolasīto baitu kopskaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4986">**Data\_FileIOBytesRead: int -** total bytes read while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4987">**Data\_FileIOBytesReadSquared: int —** Data\_FileIOBytesRead vērtība kvadrātā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4987">**Data\_FileIOBytesReadSquared: int -** squared value of Data\_FileIOBytesRead</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4988">**Data\_FileIOBytesWritten: int —** saglabāšanas laikā ierakstīto baitu kopskaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4988">**Data\_FileIOBytesWritten: int -** total bytes written while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4989">**Data\_FileIOBytesWrittenSquared: int —** Data\_FileIOBytesWritten vērtība kvadrātā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4989">**Data\_FileIOBytesWrittenSquared: int -** squared value of Data\_FileIOBytesWritten</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4990">**Data\_FileName: binary** — faila nosaukuma binārā jaukšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4990">**Data\_FileName: binary -** Binary Hash of file name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4991">**Data\_FileOpenDownloadDurationInMs: long —** faila lejupielādes laiks milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4991">**Data\_FileOpenDownloadDurationInMs: long -** duration to download file in milliseconds</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4992">**Data\_FileOpenEndDurationInMs: long —** faila atvēršanas laiks milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4992">**Data\_FileOpenEndDurationInMs: long: -** duration to open file in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4993">**Data\_FileOpenTimeStamp: time: —** laikspiedols, kad tiek sākta faila atvēršana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4993">**Data\_FileOpenTimeStamp: time: -** Time stamp when file started opening</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4994">**Data\_FilePathHash: binary** — faila ceļa GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4994">**Data\_FilePathHash: binary -** GUID for file path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4995">**Data\_FileSize: long —** dokumenta lielums baitos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4995">**Data\_FileSize: long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4996">**Data\_FileType: string —** atvērtas shēmas faila paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4996">**Data\_FileType: string -** File extension of diagram opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4997">**Data\_IsInternalFile: bool —** patiess, ja fails ir iekšējais fails</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4997">**Data\_IsInternalFile: bool -** true if file is an internal file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4998">Piemēram, šablons</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4998">e.g. Stencil</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-4999">**Data\_IsIRM: bool —** patiess, ja failam ir informācijas tiesību piekļuves aizsardzība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-4999">**Data\_IsIRM: bool -** true if file is Information Right Protected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5000">**Data\_IsReadOnly: bool —** patiess, ja fails ir tikai lasāms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5000">**Data\_IsReadOnly: bool -** true if the file is read only</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5001">**Data\_IsSuccess: bool —** patiess, ja faila atvēršana bija sekmīga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5001">**Data\_IsSuccess: bool -** true when file open was successful</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5002">**Data\_Location: string —** faila atrašanās vietas, piemēram, lokāla, SharePoint, OneDrive, WopiConsumer, WopiBusiness, GenericThirdPartyConsumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5002">**Data\_Location: string -** location of the file like Local, SharePoint, OneDrive, WopiConsumer, WopiBusiness, GenericThirdPartyConsumer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5003">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesRead: int —** saglabāšanas laikā nolasīto tīkla baitu kopskaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5003">**Data\_NetworkIOBytesRead: int -** total network bytes read while saving</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5008">**Data\_Size\_Docs: integer —** dokumenta lielums baitos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5008">**Data\_Size\_Docs: integer -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriversofthang"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5013">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5013">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5014">Palīdz Microsoft nošķirt videokartes draivera nereaģēšanas gadījumus no īsākiem gadījumiem, lai vieglāk pieņemtu lēmumus par to, kuriem videokartes draiveriem, iespējams, ir radušās problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5014">Helps Microsoft separate long video card driver hangs from short ones, which in turn helps make decisions about which video card drivers may be having problems.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5015">Lietotāja videokartes draiveris izraisīja situāciju, kurā Office pārtrauca reaģēt, taču šīs situācijas ietekme vēl nav zināma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5015">The user's video card driver has caused Office to hang, but the impact of the hang is not known yet</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5016">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5016">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5017">**Data\_InDeviceCall** — metode izsauca videokarti, kas izraisīja reaģēšanas pārtraukumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5017">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - The method called on the video card that produced the hang</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5018">**Data\_Timeout** — cik ilgi nereaģēja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5018">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted</span></span>

  #### <a name="officeandroidadalsigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5019">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5019">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5020">Šīs notikums norāda, ka lietotājs saņēma pierakstīšanās uzvedni skolas vai darba kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5020">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for school or work account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5021">Šis notikums palīdz saprast mūsu lietojumprogrammu pierakstīšanās stāvokļa darbspēju un atbilstoši rīkoties, kad pamanām neparedzētas pierakstīšanās uzvednes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5021">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5022">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5022">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5023">**LastLoginDelta** — laika delta no pēdējās sekmīgās pieteikšanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5023">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5024">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** — norāda konta stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5024">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** - Indicates the state of the account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5025">**PreviousIdentityState** — norāda konta stāvokli, piemēram, sesijas laiks beidzies.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5025">**PreviousIdentityState** - Indicates state of the account, like session expired.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5026">**SignInResultCode** — norāda pierakstīšanās uzvednes beigu rezultātā kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5026">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5027">**UseCache**— norāda, vai mēs ar uzvednes palīdzību likām lietotājam ievadīt paroli atkārtoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5027">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5028">**UserType** — norāda, vai tas ir esošs konts vai jauns konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5028">**UserType** - Indicates whether it is existing account or new account</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidappdocsfileoperationends"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5029">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5029">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5030">Kritiskie dokumenti tikai Android (AppDocs) telemetrijas dati faila jauns/atvērt/saglabāt kā beigu darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5030">Critical Docs Android Only (AppDocs) telemetry data for File New/Open/SaveAs end operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5031">Uzskaita šo AppDocs neveiksmīgo darbību kļūdu kodus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5031">This captures error codes for failures of these AppDocsOperations.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5032">Microsoft to izmanto, lai noteiktu kļūmes dažādās failu darbībā un precīzo slāni, kurā radās WXP lietojumprogrammu kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5032">Microsoft uses this to identify failures in various file operation and the exact layer at which the failure has occurred in WXP apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5033">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5033">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5034">**AccessMode** — faila piekļuves režīma uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5034">**AccessMode** - enumeration value for the access mode for the file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5035">Vērtības — nav, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5035">Values- None, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5036">**BlockingUIShown** — būla, kas norāda, vai jebkurā vietā plūsmā tika parādīts bloķēšanas lietotāja interfeiss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5036">**BlockingUIShown** - Boolean to indicate if blocking UI was shown in the flow anywhere.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5037">**ContentUriAuthority** — satura URL no SAF iestādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5037">**ContentUriAuthority** - the authority of the content URL from SAF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5038">**Correlation** — GUID ar darbību saistītajam sasaistes ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5038">**Correlation** - GUID for the correlation Id related to the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5039">**DocId** — AppDocs ģenerētais dokumenta ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5039">**DocId** - the document ID generated by AppDocs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5040">**DocInstanceId** — AppDocs ģenerētā dokumenta instances ID, kas ir ietverta darbības instancē dokumentā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5040">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5041">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** — būla, kas norāda, vai dokuments ir aizsargāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5041">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5042">**DocUserId** — lietotāja ID no MS autentifikācijas slāņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5042">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5043">**DocUserIdProvider** — uzskaitījums, kas apzīmē lietotāja ID nodrošinātāju, 0 = nezināms, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5043">**DocUserIdProvider** - enumeration that represents the user ID provider, 0 = Unkown, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5044">**DurationInMs** — faila darbības beigšanās laiks milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5044">**DurationInMs** - time in millisecond for the file operation to end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5045">**EndReason** — uzskaitījuma vērtība, kas apzīmē beigu iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5045">**EndReason** - enumeration value for the end reason.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5046">Vērtības — nav, izdevās, neizdevās, atcelt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5046">Values - None, Success, Failure, Cancel</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5047">**ErrorCode** — faila darbības kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5047">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5048">**Extension** — faila, kas tiek atvērts, paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5048">**Extension** - extension of the file being opened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5049">**FileSourceLocation** — faila atrašanās vietas uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5049">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for file location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5050">Iespējamās vērtības: nav, lokāls, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, lietojumprogramma, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5050">Possible values: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5051">**FILETIME** — notikuma laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5051">**FILETIME** - Time of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5052">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** — kļūdas koda informācija, kas saistīta ar failu konvertēšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5052">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** - Error code information related to file conversions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5053">**HttpStatusCode** — http atbildes kods tīmekļa pakalpojuma pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5053">**HttpStatusCode** - http response code for web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5054">**InitalizationReason** — faila atvēršanas ieejas punkts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5054">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5055">**K2FileIOHresult** — Hresult kods faila atvēršanas darbības beigām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5055">**K2FileIOHresult** - Hresult code for File open operation end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5056">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** — pēdējā BCS (binārā konvertēšanas pakalpojums) klienta kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5056">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5057">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** — statusa karodziņš tīmekļa pakalpojuma pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5057">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** - status flag for the web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5058">**OpEndEventId** — atzīme, kas norāda, kur faktiski beidzās darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5058">**OpEndEventId** - tag that represents where the operation actually ended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5059">**OpFlags** — dokumenta darbību param. karodziņi, ko izmanto AppDocs slānis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5059">**OpFlags** - Document operation param flags used by AppDocs layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5060">**OpSeqNum** — skaitlis, kas norāda ar failu darbību saistīto pieprasījumu secību AppDocs slānī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5060">**OpSeqNum** - A number that represents the sequencing of file operation related calls in AppDocs layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5061">**OpType** — darbības veida uzskaitījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5061">**OpType** - operation type enumeration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5062">Vērtības: "nav", "CreateDocument", "OpenDocument", "CopyDocument", "CloseDocument", "SaveDocument", "OpenVersion", "CloseVersion"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5062">Values: "None", "CreateDocument", "OpenDocument", "CopyDocument", "CloseDocument", "SaveDocument", "OpenVersion", "CloseVersion"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5063">**PreFetchState** — uzskaitījums jaunu failu izveides darbību vedņu iepriekšējās ieneses stāvoklim.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5063">**PreFetchState** - enumeration for prefetch state of templates for new file create operations.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5064">**ProviderApp** — tās lietojumprogrammas pakotnes nosaukums, no kuras tiek atvērts fails</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5064">**ProviderApp** - the package name of the app from which file is opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5065">**ScopeInstanceId** — tvēruma instances ID, kas tiek lietots datu konteksta pievienošanai darbībām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5065">**ScopeInstanceId** - Scope Instance ID used to join data context to activities</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5066">**Size** — faila lielums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5066">**Size** - file size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5067">**State** — faila stāvokļa uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5067">**State** - enumeration value for the state of the file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5068">Vērtības: nav, notiek izveide, izveidots, neizdevās izveidot, atvēršana, atvērts, atvēršana neizdevās, notiek kopēšana, kopēšana neizdevās, notiek aizvēršana, aizvērts, aizvēršana neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5068">Values: None, Creating, Created, CreateFailed, Opening, Opened, OpenFailed, Copying, Copied, CopyFailed, Closing, Closed, CloseFail</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5070">**UriScheme** — URL shēma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5070">**UriScheme** - scheme of the URL</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidautherror"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5071">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5071">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5072">Šis notikums apzīmē pamata autentifikācijas kļūmes klusās marķiera atsvaidzināšanas laikā, pakalpojuma pierakstīšanās lapas ielādes laikā un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5072">This event denotes core authentication failures during silent token refresh, loading sign in page from service and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5073">Šis notikums palīdz saprast mūsu lietojumprogrammu pierakstīšanās stāvokļa darbspēju, veiktos pierakstīšanās mēģinājumus, un atbilstoši rīkoties, kad pamanām neparedzētas kļūmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5073">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps, sign in attempts that are made, and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected failures.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5074">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5074">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5075">**ADALErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni vai kluso marķiera ieneses mēģinājumu darba kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5075">**ADALErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5076">**ADALErrorCode** — norāda neapstrādāto kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni vai kluso marķiera ieneses mēģinājumu darba kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5076">**ADALRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5077">**ErrorGroup** — norāda konta veidu, piemēram, personiskais vai darba konts vai lokālo darba kontu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5077">**ErrorGroup** - Indicates the type of account like personal account or work account or on-premise work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5078">**IDCRLErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5078">**IDCRLErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5079">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** — norāda neapstrādātu kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5079">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5080">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas kodu personiskā konta klusā marķiera atsvaidzināšanas mēģinājuma laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5080">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** - Indicates error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5081">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** — norāda neapstrādātu kļūdas kodu personiskā konta klusā marķiera atsvaidzināšanas mēģinājuma laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5081">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficeactivationlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5155">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5155">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5156">Kritiski svarīgi dati, lai apkopotu pilnvērtīgu faila atvēršanas laiku visām faila atvēršanām Windows, Excel, PowerPoint lietojumprogrammās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5156">Critical data to collect end-to-end file open time for all file opens in Windows, Excel, PowerPoint apps.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5157">Microsoft to izmanto, lai noskaidrotu mūsu lietojumprogrammu failu atvēršanas metriku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5157">This is used by Microsoft to find out the metric for file open performance of our apps</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5158">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5158">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5159">**AppBootingOccured** — būla, lai pārbaudītu, vai lietojumprogrammas sāknēšana ir pabeigta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5159">**AppBootingOccured** - Boolean to check if app boot is complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5160">**ApplicationBootTime** — lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas specifiskajai fāzei nepieciešamais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5160">**ApplicationBootTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5161">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** — būla, lai pārbaudītu, vai lietojumprogramma tika aizturēta sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5161">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to check if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5162">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** — būla, lai norādītu, vai faila atvēršanas darbības laikā bija bloķēšanas dialogs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5162">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** - Boolean to indicate if there was any blocking dialog during the file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5163">**CachedInfoAvailable** — būla, lai meklētu kešatmiņā saglabātu faila atvēršanai specifisku informāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5163">**CachedInfoAvailable** - Boolean to look for cached info specific to file open operation</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidclientsideiap"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5239">Office.Android.ClientSideIAP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5239">Office.Android.ClientSideIAP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5240">Kritisko kļūdu telemetrija datu bāzu kļūmei, pārlūkojot failus un pievienojot vietas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5240">Critical Error telemetry for Database Failure while file browsing and adds places.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5241">Microsoft to izmanto, lai identificētu datu bāzu problēmas lietojumprogrammās, kas var traucēt lietotājam pievienot vietas vai pārlūkot tās lietojumprogrammās, izmantojot WXP lietojumprogrammas. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5241">Microsoft uses this to identify DB corruption issues in the apps which might hinder user to add places or browse through them from within the app in WXP apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5242">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5242">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5243">**ClientTransactionId** — GUID, kas tiek nodots DSC specifiskam izpirkšanas pieprasījumam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5243">**ClientTransactionId** - GUID passed to DSC for a specific Redemption request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5244">**CollectionTime** — abonementa iegādes pabeigšanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5244">**CollectionTime** - time of subscription purchase completion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5245">**CountryCode** — klienta valsts kods, kas tiek nosūtīts DSC klienta izpirkšanas pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5245">**CountryCode** - Client country code which is sent to DSC for client redemption request</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5371">Kritisko kļūdu telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota O365 kontu W/X/P lietojumprogrammās licencēšanas aktivizēšanas kļūmju izsekošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5371">Critical Error telemetry to track failures to activate licenses for O365 accounts in W/X/P apps.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5372">Microsoft to izmanto, lai analizētu iegādāto O365 licenču aktivizēšanas kļūmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5372">Microsoft uses this to analyze failures to activate a purchased o365 license.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5373">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5373">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5374">**EntryPoint** — ieejas punkta uzskaitījums licenču aktivizēšanas plūsmas aktivizēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5374">**EntryPoint** - Entrypoint enumeration for triggering the license activation flow</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5375">**HResult** — kļūmes kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5375">**HResult** - error code for the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5376">**IsGallatin** — būla, kas tiek izmantota, lai pārbaudītu, vai tas ir Gallatin konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5376">**IsGallatin** - Boolean to check if it is a Gallatin account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5377">**MessageCode**— uzskaitījums, kas norāda aktivizēšanas kļūmes punktu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5377">**MessageCode** - enumeration to indicate the point of failure for activation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5378">**PreviousEntryPoint** — ieejas punkta uzskaitījums licenču aktivizēšanas plūsmas aktivizēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5378">**PreviousEntryPoint** - Entrypoint enumeration for triggering the license activation flow</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5379">**StateAfterActivation** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas stāvokli pirms aktivizēšanas plūsmas sākuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5379">**StateAfterActivation** - enumeration to indicate licensing state of the app before the activation flow started</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5380">**StateBeforeActivation** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas stāvokli pirms aktivizēšanas plūsmas sākuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5380">**StateBeforeActivation** - enumeration to indicate licensing state of the app before the activation flow started</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5381">**UserAccountType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda, vai konts ir personiskais vai uzņēmuma konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5381">**UserAccountType** - enumeration to indicate whether personal account or enterprise account.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidmsasigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5382">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5382">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5383">Šīs notikums norāda, ka lietotājs saņēma pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5383">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for personal account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5384">Šis notikums palīdz saprast mūsu lietojumprogrammu pierakstīšanās stāvokļa darbspēju un atbilstoši rīkoties, kad pamanām neparedzētas pierakstīšanās uzvednes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5384">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5385">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5385">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5386">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** — marķiera atsvaidzināšanas mēģinājuma pirms pierakstīšanās uzvednes parādīšanas kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5386">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** - Error code of token refresh attempt, before showing sign-in prompt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5387">**LastLoginDelta** — laika delta no pēdējās sekmīgās pieteikšanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5387">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5388">**MSAserverUAID** — korelācijas ID ar pakalpojuma telemetrijas datiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5388">**MSAserverUAID** - Correlation id with service telemetry data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5389">**PreviousIdentityState** — norāda konta stāvokli, piemēram, sesijas laiks beidzies.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5389">**PreviousIdentityState** - Indicates state of the account, like session expired.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5390">**SignInResultCode** — norāda pierakstīšanās uzvednes beigu rezultātā kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5390">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5391">**UseCache**— norāda, vai mēs ar uzvednes palīdzību likām lietotājam ievadīt paroli atkārtoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5391">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5392">**UserType** — norāda, vai tas ir esošs konts vai jauns konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5392">**UserType** - Indicates whether it is existing account or new account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5393">**WasIdentitySignedOut** — norāda, vai konts bija izrakstīšanās stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5393">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - Indicates if account was in signed out state.</span></span>


#### <a name="office_apple_licensing_mac_dractivationfailures"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5394">Office_Apple_Licensing_Mac_DRActivationFailures</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5394">Office_Apple_Licensing_Mac_DRActivationFailures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5395">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas tiek lietotas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5395">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5396">Pasākums tiek lietots Digital River aktivizēšanas kļūmju novēršanai (notikums reģistrē galveno un produktu, kas tika lietots aktivizācijai, kā arī saņemtās kļūdas kodu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5396">The event is used for capturing digital river activation failures (the event logs the key and product that was used to activate, as well as the error code received).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5397">Šis notikums tiek lietots, lai noteiktu un palīdzētu novērst aktivizācijas kļūmes (Digital River problēmas).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5397">This event is used for detecting and helping troubleshoot activation failures (Digital River issues).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5398">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5398">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5399">**Data_DigitalRiverID** — Digital River produkta ID, kas kartē uz šo Office produkta SKY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5399">**Data_DigitalRiverID** - Digital River product Id that maps to this Office product SKY</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5400">**Data_Error** — virkne, kas norāda aktivizācijas kļūdas kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5400">**Data_Error** - A string representing an activation error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5401">**Data_ProductKey** — produkta atslēga, ko bija mēģināts aktivizēt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5401">**Data_ProductKey** - Product key that was attempted to be activated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5423">Šī izņēmuma uzrādītā informācija ir svarīga, lai izvērtētu kopējo grafikas steka darbspēju, kā arī identificētu tās koda daļas, kur kļūmes radās ar lielu intensitāti, lai noteiktu izmeklēšanas prioritātes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5423">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, as well as identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency, in order to prioritize investigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5424">Šī izņēmuma uzrādītā informācija ir svarīga, lai izvērtētu kopējo grafikas steka darbspēju, kā arī identificētu tās koda daļas, kur kļūmes radās ar lielu intensitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5424">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, as well as identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5425">Tas palīdz inženierim noteikt, kuras atveidošanas kļūmes ietekmē lielāko daļu lietotāju, lai mēs varētu noteikt prioritātes mūsu ieguldījumiem, vēršot tos uz tādu problēmu novēršanu, kas lietotājiem sniegs vislielāko ieguvumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5425">This helps an engineer to determine which rendering failures are impacting the most users, enabling us to prioritize our investigations toward fixing issues that will have the greatest user benefit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5426">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5426">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5427">**Data\_HResult** — kļūmes atgrieztais kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5427">**Data\_HResult** - The error code returned from failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5428">**Data\_TagCount** — katras radušās kļūmes skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5428">**Data\_TagCount** - The count of each failure that occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5429">**Data\_TagID** — radušās kļūmes identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5429">**Data\_TagID** - The identifier of the failure that occurred</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5448">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5448">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5450">**1 —** Būla virkne, kas norāda, vai lietotājs izvēlas jaunu failu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5450">**1 -** Bool indicating if the user chooses new file or not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5578">**ErrorGroup** — katras kļūdas intervāla identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5578">**ErrorGroup** - A bucketing identifier for each error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5579">**ErrorId** — kļūdas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5579">**ErrorId** – An identifier for the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5581">**Trackback** — konkrētas kļūdas unikālais identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5581">**Trackback** - A unique identifier for a specific error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5583">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs mēģina atvērt ar IRM aizsargātu dokumentu vai lietot IRM aizsardzību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5583">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5584">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek, kad neizdodas lietotāja sertifikātu atjaunošana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5584">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when failed to renew user certificates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5585">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5585">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5586">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** — klienta hierarhija, kas norāda, ka lietojumprogramma darbojas ražošanas vidē vai izstrādātāja vidē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5586">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5587">**AppInfo.Name** — lietojumprogrammas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5587">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5588">**AppInfo.Version** — lietojumprogrammas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5588">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5589">**Failure.Category** — kļūmes kategorija "UnhandledError"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5589">**Failure.Category** - The category of the failure “UnhandledError”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5590">**Failure.Detail** — detalizēta informācija par kļūmi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5590">**Failure.Detail** - The detailed info of the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5591">**Failure.Id** — kļūmes ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5591">**Failure.Id** - Failure Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5592">**Failure.Signature** — kļūmes paraksts, kas ir tāds pats kā notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5592">**Failure.Signature** - The signature of the failure, which is same as the event name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5593">**iKey** — pieteikšanās pakalpojuma servera ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5593">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5594">**RMS.HRESULT** — lietotāja sertifikāta atjaunošanas rezultāts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5594">**RMS.HRESULT** - The result of renewing user certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5595">**RMS.ScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko definē tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klients</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5595">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5596">**RMS.SDKVersion** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klienta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5596">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistdriverupdated"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5602">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5602">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5603">Lietotājs atjaunināja videokartes draiveri, kas iepriekš izraisīja Office avārijas, un tas vairs netiek izmantots atveidošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5603">User has updated a video card driver that was previously causing Office crashes and thus no longer being used to render.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5604">Informē Microsoft, ka lietotājiem, kuriem bija pasliktināts atveidošanas stāvoklis, atkal ir ieteicamais atveidošanas stāvoklis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5604">Informs Microsoft that users who were once in a sub-optimal rendering state are once again in the recommended rendering state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5605">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5605">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5606">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** — bloķētā draivera versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5606">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5607">**Data\_DeviceId** — bloķētās videokartes ierīces identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5607">**Data\_DeviceId** -identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5608">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** — atjauninātā draivera versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5608">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** - Version of the updated driver</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5609">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5609">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5610">Detalizēta informācija par lietotāja videokartes draiveri, kas izraisīja vairākas nesenas Office lietojumprogrammu avārijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5610">Details on the user's video card driver that has caused multiple recent crashes of Office applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5611">Office neizmantos šo videokarti šajā Office sesijā (tā vietā izmantojot programmatūras atveidošanu), līdz draiveris būs atjaunināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5611">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5612">Informē Microsoft par videokartes draiveri, kas rada problēmas sistēmā Office, lai identificētu tendences un analizētu šādu draiveru ietekmi uz lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5612">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5613">Informējiet Microsoft, cik lietotāju ir šādā pasliktinātā stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5613">Tell Microsoft how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5614">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5614">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5615">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** — vai visas Office lietojumprogrammas ir bloķētas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5615">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** - Whether all Office apps are blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5616">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** — bloķētās videokartes ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5616">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5617">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** — bloķētā draivera versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5617">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5618">**Data\_CrashHistory** — virkne, kas attēlo videokartes draivera izraisītās avārijas, lai veiktu analīzi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5618">**Data\_CrashHistory** - A string that represents the history of video card driver caused crashes for analysis</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5622">Norit jaunākās Office zema līmeņa atveidošanas platformas izstrāde un piegāde klientiem, kas ļauj Microsoft redzēt, cik daudz lietotāju ir katrā versijā, lai nodrošinātu, ka platforma darbojas bez kļūdām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5622">As the latest Office low-level rendering platform is developed and begins to be released to customers, this allows Microsoft to see how many users are on each version to ensure the platform remains bug-free.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorblocklistapp"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5625">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5625">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5626">Lietotāja videokarte ir noteikta kā iemesls, kas izraisa ilgus vai neatkopjamus reaģēšanas pārtraukumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5626">User’s video card has been detected as causing long or unrecoverable hangs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5627">Office neizmantos šo videokarti šajā Office sesijā (tā vietā izmantojot programmatūras atveidošanu), līdz draiveris būs atjaunināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5627">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5628">Informē Microsoft par videokartes draiveri, kas rada problēmas sistēmā Office, lai identificētu tendences un analizētu šādu draiveru ietekmi uz lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5628">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5629">Palīdz arī informēt, cik lietotāju ir šādā pasliktinātā stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5629">Also helps in informing how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5630">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5630">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5631">**Data\_AppName** — kurā programmā videokartes draiveris pārtrauca reaģēt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5631">**Data\_AppName** - Which app has encountered video card driver hangs</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorregistrywrite"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5632">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5632">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5633">Office konstatēja, ka lietotāja videokartes draiveris izraisīja reaģēšanas pārtraukumu, kas ir jāanalizē nākamajā Office lietojumprogrammas startēšanas reizē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5633">Office has identified that the user's video card driver has caused a hang that should be analyzed at the next Office application boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5634">Izmanto, lai noteiktu, vai cits videokartes draiveris vai adapteris nodrošina labāku lietotāja pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5634">Used to determine whether using a different video card driver or adapter would offer a better user experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5635">Shēmu izpildes laikā Microsoft var veikt pielāgojumus, lai Office pieredzi saglabātu iespējami netraucētu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5635">As patterns occur, Microsoft may make adjustments to keep the Office experience as smooth as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5636">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5636">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5637">**Data\_HangDetected** — vai tika konstatēts reaģēšanas pārtraukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5637">**Data\_HangDetected** - Whether a hang was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5638">**Data\_InDeviceCall** — kādu videokartes atveidošanas izsaukumu veica Office, kad tā pārtrauca reaģēt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5638">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - Which video card rendering call Office was in when the hang occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5639">**Data\_Timeout** — cik ilgi nereaģēja, ja notika atkopšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5639">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted, if it recovered</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5640">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** — vai reaģēšanas pārtraukumu šajā videokartes atveidošanas komandā parasti iespējams atkopt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5640">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** - Whether the hang in this video card rendering command is typically recoverable.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5651">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** — cik bieži avarē draivera karte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5651">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** - How frequently driver card crashes are occurring</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32localblocklistdriverupdatedactivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5652">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistDriverUpdatedActivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5652">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistDriverUpdatedActivity</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5656">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** — bloķētās videokartes ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5656">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

#### <a name="officegraphicsspritememcorrupt"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5659">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5659">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5660">Uzrāda visas kļūdas, kas konstatētas Sprite atmiņas uzskaites telemetrijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5660">Reports any errors detected in the sprite memory accounting telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5661">Kritiski svarīgi, lai novērtētu grafikas atmiņas lietojuma telemetrijas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5661">Critical for assessing health of the graphics memory usage telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5662">Šī informācija ir nepieciešama, lai validētu mūsu SpriteMem telemetrijas datu pareizību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5662">This information is needed to validate the correctness of our SpriteMem telemetry.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5663">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5663">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5664">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** — kopējais atmiņas apjoms, kas tiek aktīvi piešķirta, lai noturētu Sprite objektus (attēlus), radot ekrāna saturu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5664">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** - Total amount of memory that is actively allocated to hold sprites (images) that result in screen content.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5665">**Data\_Function** — funkcijas nosaukums, kas mēģina atbrīvot Sprite atmiņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5665">**Data\_Function** - The name of the function that is attempting to release sprite memory.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5666">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** — atmiņas apjoms, kas jānoņem no Sprite sadalījuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5666">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** - Amount of memory to be removed from sprite allocation.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptsharednointernetconnectivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5667">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5667">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5668">Apkopo katru reizi, kad PowerPoint konstatē, ka nav interneta savienojuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5668">Collected whenever PowerPoint detects there is no internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5669">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai iegūtu diagnostikas informāciju par lietotāja interneta savienojumu un izprastu, kā tas ietekmē savienojumu ar Office pakalpojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5669">Microsoft uses this data to get diagnostic information about the user's internet connection to be able to understand how that impacts connectivity to Office services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5670">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5670">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5671">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** – redzams, vai ir interneta savienojuma statuss, izsaucot Nexus pakalpojumu (patiesa vērtība) vai izsaucot standarta tīmekļa pakalpojuma API (aplama vērtība)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5671">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** - shows whether we got the Internet connectivity status when calling Nexus service (value true) or when calling generic web service API call (value false)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerofficesvcmgrprofile"></a><span data-ttu-id="ef881-5672">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5672">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5673">Notikums sākas brīdi, kad tiek sāknēts Office Serviceability Manager, un ir kritiski svarīgs, lai sniegtu ieskatu saistībā ar izvietošanas statusu, lietojumprogrammu un pievienojumprogrammu avārijām klienta nomniekā, ļaujot mums ģenerēt ieskatus, lai IT administrators spētu pārliecināti veidot atjauninājumus sava uzņēmumam datoriem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5673">This event is triggered when Office Serviceability Manager starts, and is critical for providing accurate insights related to Deployment Status and Application and Add-in crashes within customer's tenant by allowing us to generate insights for the IT Admin to be able to confidently roll-out updates for their enterprise machines.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="ef881-5674">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5674">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5675">**DeviceIdJoinToken** — tiek izmantots, lai savienotu telemetrijas datus darbspējas un izvietošanas statusa ar citiem funkcionāliem datiem, kas tiek iegūti no pakalpojumu konveijera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5675">**DeviceIdJoinToken** - used to join Telemetry data from Health and Deployment Status with other Functional Data which is collected via the Services pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ef881-5676">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** — būlas karodziņš, kas tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu Office ekosistēmā pārvaldīto ierīču skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef881-5676">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** - a Boolean flag used to determine the number of Managed devices in the Office eco-system.</span></span>
